WEBVTT

00:00:01.535 --> 00:00:06.015
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

00:00:14.692 --> 00:00:19.581
What is truth? We do not know.

00:00:22.110 --> 00:00:26.493
We have our own concept about truth.

00:00:26.522 --> 00:00:28.902
With our mental projections

00:00:28.902 --> 00:00:33.842
we think truth is that we are human beings,

00:00:33.851 --> 00:00:37.021
that we have to live on this earth,

00:00:37.031 --> 00:00:39.311
look after our children,

00:00:39.311 --> 00:00:41.081
look after the family,

00:00:41.081 --> 00:00:44.451
live well and die, that’s all.

00:00:45.105 --> 00:00:47.605
We do not know the truth is

00:00:47.605 --> 00:00:49.985
that we are the Spirit.

00:00:49.991 --> 00:00:53.425
That we have experienced
yesterday, that you are the Spirit.

00:00:54.435 --> 00:00:56.645
But we do not know also an other thing

00:00:56.645 --> 00:01:01.145
that God has created this universe

00:01:01.165 --> 00:01:04.455
and created you with very great care

00:01:04.476 --> 00:01:07.485
and with tremendous love.

00:01:07.495 --> 00:01:11.285
Truth is love because that’s the fact:

00:01:11.297 --> 00:01:14.385
that because he loved us so much,

00:01:14.403 --> 00:01:16.575
he really loved us so much

00:01:16.575 --> 00:01:23.650
that he created us on this earth and
evolved us to this state of a human being.

00:01:23.650 --> 00:01:25.880
We take him for granted,

00:01:25.890 --> 00:01:29.380
everything that he has done for us.

00:01:29.403 --> 00:01:32.780
We have no idea as to how much care

00:01:32.780 --> 00:01:37.390
he has taken to develop us out
of the evolutionary process

00:01:37.373 --> 00:01:39.680
to this state of a human being

00:01:39.684 --> 00:01:43.070
which is the epitome of his Creation.

00:01:46.163 --> 00:01:51.605
When Eve and Adam made a mistake

00:01:51.614 --> 00:01:56.166
they really gave a big trouble to the divine,

00:01:56.186 --> 00:01:59.526
because if they had not made a mistake

00:01:59.526 --> 00:02:04.010
and had confidence and
gratitude for the love of God

00:02:04.980 --> 00:02:07.236
they would have not
committed such a mistake

00:02:07.236 --> 00:02:11.426
is to know about the knowledge.

00:02:11.450 --> 00:02:15.546
The knowledge which they wanted
to know through their ego,

00:02:15.566 --> 00:02:19.306
knowledge that they wanted to
know through their efforts.

00:02:19.316 --> 00:02:23.443
Because of this simple
mistake that they committed

00:02:23.448 --> 00:02:29.599
we had to undergo all these processes.

00:02:29.629 --> 00:02:33.219
That’s how we had to go through
the evolutionary process,

00:02:33.241 --> 00:02:36.609
come to this state and become human beings,

00:02:36.630 --> 00:02:41.211
understanding that we have
to become the Spirit.

00:02:41.226 --> 00:02:44.636
But at that state if you had listened

00:02:44.656 --> 00:02:48.566
and had faith in God’s love,

00:02:48.576 --> 00:02:51.316
we would have been much better off.

00:02:51.336 --> 00:02:54.885
There would have been no
problem of evolution or anything,

00:02:54.911 --> 00:02:57.411
because it is very easy for God

00:02:57.411 --> 00:03:00.275
to create you as whatever way he wants.

00:03:00.275 --> 00:03:02.775
But he had to make you pass through

00:03:02.775 --> 00:03:05.875
all this evolutionary process

00:03:05.880 --> 00:03:07.815
through your own projections,

00:03:07.815 --> 00:03:10.455
through your own misunderstandings,

00:03:10.457 --> 00:03:12.957
through your own trials and errors,

00:03:12.948 --> 00:03:16.122
till you reached the state
that is a human being.

00:03:16.132 --> 00:03:18.962
So now no more mistakes
have to be committed.

00:03:18.979 --> 00:03:23.159
Now we have reached the state
where we can become the Spirit.

00:03:23.190 --> 00:03:25.690
But here also, as the human nature is

00:03:25.690 --> 00:03:30.790
that we always try to do things
which we are not supposed to do.

00:03:30.807 --> 00:03:33.142
Moses came on this Earth to teach us

00:03:33.142 --> 00:03:35.463
that we should do not do these....

00:03:35.477 --> 00:03:40.271
Ten Commandments are
not to be crossed over.

00:03:40.311 --> 00:03:44.461
He gave us the Commandments that
we should lead a life of balance.

00:03:45.481 --> 00:03:48.241
But it seems that the balance

00:03:48.241 --> 00:03:51.341
that he tried to create within us

00:03:51.361 --> 00:03:54.371
is being completely flouted,

00:03:54.381 --> 00:03:58.811
challenged and absolutely

00:03:58.837 --> 00:04:01.840
given up by many human beings.

00:04:01.876 --> 00:04:04.376
They don’t think it is necessary to have

00:04:04.376 --> 00:04:06.100
those Ten Commandments,

00:04:06.100 --> 00:04:08.600
which were to maintain our valency

00:04:08.600 --> 00:04:13.920
in our being

00:04:13.947 --> 00:04:19.515
so that we can ascend, because
without a balance we cannot ascend.

00:04:19.515 --> 00:04:22.015
That’s a simple thing we must understand.

00:04:22.015 --> 00:04:24.415
We do not understand many things,

00:04:24.415 --> 00:04:26.575
but we must understand one thing simple

00:04:26.575 --> 00:04:29.075
is that, that without a balance

00:04:29.114 --> 00:04:32.220
we cannot ascend.

00:04:32.244 --> 00:04:34.744
If you have an airplane if it has no balance

00:04:34.744 --> 00:04:39.360
it cannot ascend. In the same way
you have to have that balance within you.

00:04:39.360 --> 00:04:47.158
Then people tried to teach in balance
in various types of their incarnations,

00:04:47.158 --> 00:04:53.268
various....   various types of their manifestations.

00:04:54.138 --> 00:04:56.508
But whenever they tried to do something

00:04:56.508 --> 00:04:58.928
people just did the opposite of it.

00:04:58.928 --> 00:05:00.628
As I told you about Christ

00:05:00.628 --> 00:05:03.288
how they never listened to what he said

00:05:03.305 --> 00:05:05.805
and started a very organised religion

00:05:05.805 --> 00:05:12.568
paying no attention whatsoever to
self-actualisation or self-realisation

00:05:12.568 --> 00:05:15.278
which he talked again and again.

00:05:15.298 --> 00:05:17.368
And those who tried to use that

00:05:17.374 --> 00:05:22.038
self-opinionated themselves and
said that, “We are twice born.”

00:05:22.038 --> 00:05:25.174
Like that we have been deceiving
ourselves all the time,

00:05:25.197 --> 00:05:29.782
because you must know this intellect
has a capacity to cheat to itself,

00:05:29.782 --> 00:05:32.407
it can cheat, it can give you explanations.

00:05:32.423 --> 00:05:36.645
Be careful about it! That it is
so sharp that it can cheat you.

00:05:36.665 --> 00:05:41.325
It’s like a computer, which if it
is overgrown it can destroy us.

00:05:41.325 --> 00:05:45.065
In the same way our own
intellect can destroy us

00:05:45.065 --> 00:05:51.875
and give us wrong ideas, by which we really
try to destroy ourselves day by day.

00:05:51.856 --> 00:05:56.051
Under these circumstances one
thing one has to remember:

00:05:56.068 --> 00:06:01.071
that God Almighty has loved us,
in his love he has created us.

00:06:01.074 --> 00:06:03.574
He loves us, he is the Father

00:06:03.574 --> 00:06:06.074
who is the last word

00:06:06.074 --> 00:06:10.094
as far as the father’s
affections are concerned.

00:06:10.094 --> 00:06:13.693
He is the greatest of greatest
compassionate father,

00:06:13.693 --> 00:06:16.314
who wants you to
enter into his kingdom

00:06:16.314 --> 00:06:19.164
and enjoy the bliss of his creation.

00:06:19.164 --> 00:06:22.085
He’s not created you just to be wasted,

00:06:22.109 --> 00:06:24.715
to be frittered away,
to be thrown away,

00:06:24.721 --> 00:06:28.095
to be in the hell all your lives.

00:06:28.105 --> 00:06:30.535
He has made you, to respect you,

00:06:30.535 --> 00:06:34.025
to love you and to give
you what you deserve.

00:06:34.040 --> 00:06:38.715
The problem is we do not believe in
ourselves, we do not love ourselves.

00:06:38.715 --> 00:06:42.860
How can we then love
God who has created us?

00:06:42.890 --> 00:06:46.950
This is the biggest problem. And when we
love ourselves we become really selfish.

00:06:46.961 --> 00:06:50.210
And when we become selfish
we destroy ourselves more,

00:06:50.210 --> 00:06:53.240
because that is like
love-hate relationship

00:06:53.240 --> 00:06:57.180
I say,  that actually you
hate yourself to be selfish.

00:06:57.180 --> 00:06:59.600
Because selfishness
one can never enjoy.

00:06:59.600 --> 00:07:02.000
It is a joyless pursuit.

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:05.500
That’s why one has to understand, that

00:07:05.495 --> 00:07:07.995
first and foremost understanding

00:07:07.995 --> 00:07:12.185
should come to us that God
has created this Universe,

00:07:12.185 --> 00:07:14.685
the whole thing for us;

00:07:14.685 --> 00:07:20.255
and he has created this
beautiful instrument within us

00:07:20.275 --> 00:07:24.865
to have our second birth, to know him,

00:07:24.855 --> 00:07:27.745
to know his greatness,
to know his powers

00:07:27.745 --> 00:07:32.175
and to be the master of
those powers that he had.

00:07:32.175 --> 00:07:38.725
Any father or mother is always happy
when he can give away all that he has.

00:07:38.733 --> 00:07:42.535
So this is why we do not rely on him,

00:07:42.535 --> 00:07:44.548
we rely upon ourselves.

00:07:44.548 --> 00:07:47.215
But as long as we rely upon ourselves,

00:07:47.224 --> 00:07:52.223
we live in the realm of cause and effect,

00:07:52.240 --> 00:07:56.361
we cannot get out of it,
we cannot jump out of it.

00:07:56.361 --> 00:07:59.990
To jump out of the realm
of cause and effect

00:07:59.990 --> 00:08:02.583
one must first of all know

00:08:02.613 --> 00:08:06.073
fully well that it is God’s love,

00:08:06.093 --> 00:08:09.483
in any case he is going to save us,

00:08:09.521 --> 00:08:13.893
he is going to look after us,
he is going to worry about us.

00:08:13.910 --> 00:08:17.813
Believe that he exists as a living God.

00:08:17.847 --> 00:08:21.293
It is very difficult for
ego-oriented society

00:08:21.317 --> 00:08:23.817
to accept such a concept, that

00:08:23.817 --> 00:08:27.387
there is God still living, when
science says, "There is no God."

00:08:27.387 --> 00:08:29.517
What is the limitation of science?

00:08:29.530 --> 00:08:32.632
We do not know. I was
myself studying medicine

00:08:32.672 --> 00:08:36.548
and I was surprised they had no idea
about parasympathetic nervous system.

00:08:36.548 --> 00:08:40.218
They cannot explain many things, so
many things they just cannot explain.

00:08:40.218 --> 00:08:42.718
Whatever they see also
they cannot explain.

00:08:42.718 --> 00:08:46.088
We really cannot explain
otherwise also anything.

00:08:46.088 --> 00:08:51.657
If I ask you how a flower is made, like a
rose on a particular tree, can you explain?

00:08:51.657 --> 00:08:54.857
If I ask you how seeds sprouts,

00:08:54.897 --> 00:08:57.507
when you place it with the
Mother Earth, can you explain?

00:08:57.507 --> 00:09:00.107
Can you explain any living thing

00:09:00.107 --> 00:09:05.824
like, we can say, a child who is an
Australian will be born to an Australian?

00:09:05.824 --> 00:09:09.507
Who does all these different kinds of choices?

00:09:09.531 --> 00:09:11.491
Who works out all these things,

00:09:11.491 --> 00:09:15.861
thousands and thousands, millions and
millions and billions and billions,

00:09:15.891 --> 00:09:18.631
every year, every time?
What is that power?

00:09:18.631 --> 00:09:24.932
Let us open our heart to that great
power that is the love of God.

00:09:24.943 --> 00:09:28.212
We in our ego have become so small

00:09:28.212 --> 00:09:31.042
that we have denied his powers

00:09:31.042 --> 00:09:33.892
and we do not want to
accept that he exists.

00:09:33.922 --> 00:09:37.652
This is a very wrong thing. Of
course, to add to that as I said,

00:09:37.652 --> 00:09:40.152
there are so many fake
people in the name of God;

00:09:40.152 --> 00:09:43.627
there are so many fake organisations;

00:09:43.627 --> 00:09:47.057
there are so many fake theories and

00:09:47.064 --> 00:09:49.157
ideologies and philosophies

00:09:49.157 --> 00:09:51.367
that a person gets really surprised

00:09:51.380 --> 00:09:53.767
that these people talk
of such big things,

00:09:53.767 --> 00:09:57.587
about God’s love while they
are so selfish, so low,

00:09:57.592 --> 00:10:03.229
so narrow-minded.

00:10:03.234 --> 00:10:06.769
How can these fanatics be near God?

00:10:06.779 --> 00:10:09.918
So they should not
malign the name of God

00:10:09.938 --> 00:10:12.278
because whatever is wrong is wrong.

00:10:12.278 --> 00:10:14.778
But they are using the
name of God because that

00:10:14.778 --> 00:10:18.328
name is such that it is so pure.

00:10:18.353 --> 00:10:20.853
Anybody who wants to
do something wrong

00:10:20.853 --> 00:10:24.648
always takes up a role of a very saintly person,

00:10:24.648 --> 00:10:30.213
because then only he can
hide that ugliness outside.

00:10:30.220 --> 00:10:31.693
So we have to understand

00:10:31.686 --> 00:10:34.186
that the love of God within ourselves

00:10:34.186 --> 00:10:37.185
which works out beautiful things

00:10:37.208 --> 00:10:40.095
also works out this Realisation.

00:10:40.112 --> 00:10:43.655
It is he who works out this Realisation.

00:10:43.663 --> 00:10:46.163
It is not that we are working it out;

00:10:46.163 --> 00:10:49.281
it is going to be worked out by his power,

00:10:49.308 --> 00:10:53.231
because he wants you to enter
into the Kingdom of God.

00:10:53.231 --> 00:11:00.061
The Kingdom of God in our
being is in the limbic area,

00:11:00.061 --> 00:11:03.251
as you see here on top
of the Agnya Chakra.

00:11:03.251 --> 00:11:05.751
This is the Gate of
Christ and beyond that

00:11:05.751 --> 00:11:12.729
is the Kingdom of God
where we have to enter,

00:11:12.782 --> 00:11:15.033
this Kundalini has to enter there.

00:11:15.033 --> 00:11:17.533
And when she enters
that through it,

00:11:17.533 --> 00:11:20.033
it pierces and comes out

00:11:20.033 --> 00:11:23.323
into the subtle, gets
connected to the subtle

00:11:23.323 --> 00:11:28.843
and then you start feeling the
All-pervading power of God’s love.

00:11:28.873 --> 00:11:34.793
That’s the compassion, it is the
love that is God, that is truth.

00:11:34.793 --> 00:11:37.293
But you’ll be amazed that this power

00:11:37.293 --> 00:11:40.816
has all the powers in it embedded.

00:11:40.866 --> 00:11:43.366
For example it has all the powers

00:11:43.366 --> 00:11:46.436
which we call vital
powers or Prana Shakti

00:11:46.466 --> 00:11:48.966
which is on the right
hand side, prana shakti,

00:11:48.966 --> 00:11:51.576
 by which we exist,
by which we act,

00:11:51.606 --> 00:11:57.024
by which we work out all our desires.

00:11:57.063 --> 00:12:00.324
And on the left hand is the power of desire,

00:12:00.334 --> 00:12:02.834
that is also in it. That’s why

00:12:02.834 --> 00:12:05.754
when you become that power

00:12:05.774 --> 00:12:09.854
then what happens, your desires are automatically fulfilled.

00:12:09.854 --> 00:12:12.354
You don’t have to desire even, without

00:12:12.354 --> 00:12:14.854
desiring you’ll be surprised that

00:12:14.854 --> 00:12:18.576
you have to have something
which comes before you.

00:12:18.604 --> 00:12:23.497
It can be explained if you see
the lives of many great men.

00:12:23.527 --> 00:12:25.707
They lived with very little things

00:12:25.718 --> 00:12:27.877
but they were such satisfied souls

00:12:27.877 --> 00:12:31.827
and they never bothered about
what is going to happen to them,

00:12:31.830 --> 00:12:33.650
how they are going to be fulfilled,

00:12:33.650 --> 00:12:35.480
how things are going to work out.

00:12:35.480 --> 00:12:39.600
They never planned all these things,
everything came their way and they did it.

00:12:39.600 --> 00:12:42.100
They knew what was going to happen,

00:12:42.100 --> 00:12:45.127
what was their purpose of life
and what they had to achieve.

00:12:45.132 --> 00:12:48.567
For incarnations like Christ he
knew he was to be crucified,

00:12:48.567 --> 00:12:50.287
 he knew he had to be dead

00:12:50.282 --> 00:12:53.157
because this narrow gate has to be
crossed

00:12:53.157 --> 00:12:56.597
and that has to be crossed only by

00:12:56.607 --> 00:13:01.037
the energy itself which we
call the energy of Pranava,

00:13:01.056 --> 00:13:05.890
the energy of Chaitanya, the energy
of Logos, as they call it Ruh

00:13:05.986 --> 00:13:09.777
is the energy which is just a
sound,

00:13:09.782 --> 00:13:11.707
what we call as Omkara.

00:13:11.707 --> 00:13:14.787
That energy it was
which came on this earth

00:13:14.787 --> 00:13:18.847
and that’s why he could
walk on the water,

00:13:18.859 --> 00:13:21.359
he could walk because
he was just that energy

00:13:21.359 --> 00:13:23.859
and he could walk. He had no problem

00:13:23.859 --> 00:13:28.519
about walking on the water
because he was just an energy

00:13:28.519 --> 00:13:31.019
forming a body.

00:13:31.019 --> 00:13:33.519
That is the reason also he could

00:13:33.519 --> 00:13:37.084
resurrect because he
was just an energy,

00:13:37.104 --> 00:13:39.421
he was not matter.

00:13:39.421 --> 00:13:43.349
Because he was matter he could resurrect.

00:13:43.371 --> 00:13:46.221
And this is one thing,
was said by Shri Krishna

00:13:46.221 --> 00:13:49.441
before Christ came onto this earth

00:13:49.483 --> 00:13:51.983
that this energy does not die,

00:13:51.983 --> 00:13:55.590
it cannot be killed, it cannot be perished,

00:13:55.590 --> 00:14:00.840
it is eternal. And this eternal
life came on this earth as Christ

00:14:00.840 --> 00:14:02.780
as described by Shri Krishna.

00:14:02.755 --> 00:14:05.255
Shri Krishna was another incarnation

00:14:05.255 --> 00:14:08.870
who did so much to our awareness

00:14:08.870 --> 00:14:14.012
that he developed this centre within
us which we call as Vishuddhi chakra.

00:14:14.012 --> 00:14:16.850
I need not today tell you
about all these incarnations,

00:14:16.850 --> 00:14:19.350
how they are related to each other and

00:14:19.350 --> 00:14:22.840
how they work it out because
you’ll find out from the books

00:14:22.840 --> 00:14:28.430
and other Sahaja Yogis all the
details about how they work out,

00:14:28.430 --> 00:14:30.380
how they are joined together

00:14:30.380 --> 00:14:32.500
how they are one with each other,

00:14:32.500 --> 00:14:36.140
how they are in concord and
they had no problem about it.

00:14:36.151 --> 00:14:39.170
And also about all other

00:14:39.170 --> 00:14:42.341
angels who reside within ourselves.

00:14:42.351 --> 00:14:44.851
Now for example on the right hand side

00:14:44.851 --> 00:14:47.351
you see the yellow line – this is

00:14:47.351 --> 00:14:51.261
where the angel we
call Gabriel resides,

00:14:51.261 --> 00:14:54.881
he’s called in the...  Let it be
(Shri Mataji speaks to someone on the side)

00:14:54.881 --> 00:14:57.381
It's all right they can see.

00:14:57.381 --> 00:14:59.881
Which is called

00:14:59.881 --> 00:15:03.181
in Sanskrit as Hanumana,

00:15:03.191 --> 00:15:05.111
that is on the right hand side.

00:15:05.111 --> 00:15:08.691
The left hand side power

00:15:08.704 --> 00:15:11.906
is looked after by another angel

00:15:11.922 --> 00:15:14.036
whom we call as Saint Michael

00:15:14.036 --> 00:15:17.016
and in Sanskrit he is called as Bhairava.

00:15:17.036 --> 00:15:18.496
All these exist there.

00:15:18.539 --> 00:15:21.039
Now if I say that somebody

00:15:21.039 --> 00:15:23.539
exists, say here –
Vishuddhi, Shri Krishna

00:15:23.539 --> 00:15:27.419
or if I say that Christ exists here,

00:15:27.439 --> 00:15:30.839
how are you to believe?
We have to now prove it

00:15:30.849 --> 00:15:33.939
and you can now prove it by Kundalini action.

00:15:33.939 --> 00:15:38.501
When the Kundalini rises you didn’t
feel the raising of the Kundalini

00:15:38.501 --> 00:15:40.861
because there was no obstruction.

00:15:40.861 --> 00:15:43.611
But now you will gradually
find that Kundalini will

00:15:43.611 --> 00:15:46.891
again settle back and you’ll
start feeling your obstructions

00:15:46.891 --> 00:15:49.391
wherever you have. That’s
why at least a month

00:15:49.391 --> 00:15:51.891
is needed for you to release

00:15:51.891 --> 00:15:54.391
the energy in such a way

00:15:54.391 --> 00:15:56.891
that the Kundalini really gets fixed up

00:15:56.891 --> 00:15:59.391
and you get established.

00:15:59.391 --> 00:16:01.120
Now when the Kundalini rises

00:16:01.115 --> 00:16:04.000
then supposing it is
stuck up here [Agnya]

00:16:04.025 --> 00:16:05.900
then you to say the Lord’s Prayer

00:16:05.921 --> 00:16:09.114
whether you are a Hindu, Muslim or a Christian,

00:16:09.114 --> 00:16:13.121
you have to say the Lord’s Prayer
for this Kundalini to go up.

00:16:13.121 --> 00:16:15.134
Supposing it is stuck here [Vishuddhi]

00:16:15.144 --> 00:16:17.764
then you have to take the
name of Shri Krishna.

00:16:17.786 --> 00:16:20.201
But only a realised soul can do it.

00:16:20.201 --> 00:16:24.346
If a non-realised soul takes
the name has no effect,

00:16:24.362 --> 00:16:27.072
because you are not yet
connected with those deities.

00:16:28.002 --> 00:16:33.332
So many people who just
go and pray to God,

00:16:33.332 --> 00:16:36.552
“Oh, God, do this for me!
Oh, God, do that for me!”

00:16:36.569 --> 00:16:39.069
always go on ordering God must know

00:16:39.069 --> 00:16:42.762
that God is not in your pocket,

00:16:42.785 --> 00:16:45.285
you have to enter into his Kingdom.

00:16:45.285 --> 00:16:49.532
Say now you are in the
Kingdom of New Zealand,

00:16:49.556 --> 00:16:52.056
so your government is
looking after you.

00:16:52.056 --> 00:16:55.302
In the same way when you
enter into the Kingdom of God

00:16:55.322 --> 00:16:57.252
then only he is going
to look after you.

00:16:57.280 --> 00:17:01.067
Only by praying to God or
saying “do this” and “do that”

00:17:01.097 --> 00:17:02.197
why should he do it?

00:17:02.234 --> 00:17:05.427
Because you do not have not
the connection with him.

00:17:05.427 --> 00:17:12.004
You haven’t done the protocol of
meeting the Divine within you.

00:17:12.004 --> 00:17:13.692
And when that works out,

00:17:13.691 --> 00:17:16.191
when that divinity starts
working within you

00:17:16.191 --> 00:17:19.462
then you are amazed that
how powerful you are,

00:17:19.462 --> 00:17:21.962
how many powers rise within you

00:17:21.962 --> 00:17:25.712
and how you become a great personality.

00:17:25.750 --> 00:17:29.102
And this is an actualization;
this is a reality

00:17:29.102 --> 00:17:33.341
which must be established.

00:17:33.341 --> 00:17:35.841
It is not that you can just

00:17:35.841 --> 00:17:38.341
believe what I am saying or talking

00:17:38.341 --> 00:17:40.841
but you can see for
yourself that it works,

00:17:40.841 --> 00:17:46.949
it works. It not only works but it
establishes your complete faith in God

00:17:46.967 --> 00:17:49.709
and this faith in God is not a blind faith

00:17:49.709 --> 00:17:52.209
like people talk about God, God, God

00:17:52.209 --> 00:17:54.259
and there is nothing to be known about.

00:17:54.264 --> 00:17:56.949
Every word that I’ve said you can verify.

00:17:57.919 --> 00:18:00.419
For example, if you put
your hands towards me

00:18:00.419 --> 00:18:03.199
and ask a question,
“Mother, is there God?”

00:18:04.389 --> 00:18:06.889
Ask the question three times,
if you are a realised soul

00:18:06.889 --> 00:18:09.389
you’ll get lots of vibrations,
just like a computer.

00:18:09.389 --> 00:18:13.831
But supposing you ask a question
about a person who is not good,

00:18:13.831 --> 00:18:16.631
who is not godly, “Is that person a saint?”

00:18:16.631 --> 00:18:19.461
you might even get a little
blister on your hand.

00:18:20.991 --> 00:18:23.491
It’s so much there that
your hands feel it,

00:18:23.491 --> 00:18:27.271
start speaking. But you have
to master the technique.

00:18:28.401 --> 00:18:30.901
You have to master the
technique and which will take

00:18:30.901 --> 00:18:33.001
not more than a month as I said.

00:18:33.001 --> 00:18:36.761
It’s not a course but it’s a
state of mind where you reach.

00:18:37.504 --> 00:18:40.441
So a Self-realisation
takes place. What happens?

00:18:40.441 --> 00:18:44.015
First of all, you know about yourself,

00:18:44.015 --> 00:18:46.031
yourself means your centres;

00:18:46.031 --> 00:18:48.051
first of all, to begin with,

00:18:48.052 --> 00:18:50.871
that is you start
feeling your own centres.

00:18:50.871 --> 00:18:54.050
You start understanding
what’s wrong with you.

00:18:54.050 --> 00:18:56.601
For example, if somebody says,

00:18:56.630 --> 00:18:59.341
“Mother, it’s wrong here,
something.” That means

00:18:59.341 --> 00:19:03.701
the person has ego but he
won’t say that he has got ego.

00:19:03.701 --> 00:19:06.471
What he says, “Mother, my
Agnya chakra is catching.”

00:19:06.491 --> 00:19:09.771
If he says, “My Agnya
chakra is catching.”

00:19:09.791 --> 00:19:12.291
means his ego is overlapping

00:19:12.291 --> 00:19:16.451
so you have to turn the Agnya
chakra and the ego comes down.

00:19:16.478 --> 00:19:20.711
When we do not forgive others,
it is because we are adamant

00:19:20.711 --> 00:19:22.461
and we are in an ego state.

00:19:22.461 --> 00:19:26.481
But supposing we forgive that
person, ego just drops down.

00:19:26.485 --> 00:19:28.481
Because we have a hurt ego,

00:19:28.481 --> 00:19:30.211
we are hurt by a person,

00:19:30.211 --> 00:19:32.711
our ego is hurt, it is bloated up

00:19:32.711 --> 00:19:36.267
and we cannot forgive
because it is too much,

00:19:36.267 --> 00:19:38.767
you cannot bear it.
But if you just forgive

00:19:38.767 --> 00:19:42.551
the whole thing drops out and
you feel absolutely relaxed

00:19:42.551 --> 00:19:47.592
and you start feeling the vibrations,
the cool breeze on your hands

00:19:48.422 --> 00:19:51.431
This is what is the first
thing that happens to you

00:19:51.431 --> 00:19:55.959
as Dr Warren has told you that
you become collectively conscious,

00:19:55.959 --> 00:20:00.031
means you become. Again to
understand the word “become”,

00:20:00.031 --> 00:20:02.499
means that on your
central nervous [system]

00:20:02.499 --> 00:20:06.059
you start feeling the
vibrations of another person.

00:20:06.909 --> 00:20:09.124
Now the person who is
not a realised soul

00:20:09.124 --> 00:20:11.624
if you ask him to put
his hand on your head

00:20:11.624 --> 00:20:13.469
he won’t feel the cool breeze

00:20:13.504 --> 00:20:15.449
but a person who is a realised soul

00:20:15.449 --> 00:20:19.344
has developed that experiencing
power on his hands,

00:20:19.344 --> 00:20:21.379
he can feel the real cool breeze.

00:20:21.379 --> 00:20:24.069
Maybe sometimes a person
who is not realised

00:20:24.069 --> 00:20:25.729
is sensitive person, might be.

00:20:25.723 --> 00:20:30.399
But the amount of feeling, the
person who has experienced the Self

00:20:30.399 --> 00:20:35.623
will have will not be discernible in
a person who’s not got Realisation.

00:20:35.623 --> 00:20:38.123
Now this feeling

00:20:38.123 --> 00:20:40.509
that we have of the vibrations

00:20:40.509 --> 00:20:43.009
is related to the truth.

00:20:43.009 --> 00:20:45.835
So now in the beginning,

00:20:45.859 --> 00:20:50.065
as I told you, I had seven hippies and

00:20:50.073 --> 00:20:55.258
one sensible man with me
in England for four years

00:20:55.258 --> 00:20:57.758
and I was struggling with them.

00:20:58.848 --> 00:21:02.158
And this gentleman who
was a sensible man

00:21:02.158 --> 00:21:06.118
was very much a doubting
type, a doubting Thomas

00:21:06.150 --> 00:21:08.378
and he said to me …

00:21:08.378 --> 00:21:10.568
Now he is a great Sahaja
Yogi but at that time

00:21:10.596 --> 00:21:15.698
so he said, “Alright, Mother, I want to know
what’s wrong with my mother... with my father.”

00:21:15.718 --> 00:21:17.818
So I told him, “It’s very easy.

00:21:17.818 --> 00:21:20.318
You just put your hands like
this and ask the question.”

00:21:20.318 --> 00:21:22.818
He asked the question,
“What’s wrong with my father?”

00:21:22.818 --> 00:21:27.334
and he got a burning on this
finger here [right index].

00:21:27.334 --> 00:21:31.838
These are the centres of your father.

00:21:31.838 --> 00:21:36.028
Gone down with very bad bronchitis,
this was my synthesis.

00:21:36.051 --> 00:21:38.248
He telephones to his father,

00:21:38.248 --> 00:21:40.378
the mother came on the
phone and she said,

00:21:40.378 --> 00:21:44.508
“Your father is down with
very bad bronchitis.”

00:21:44.508 --> 00:21:47.008
He was amazed, he
said, “Now what to do?”

00:21:47.008 --> 00:21:49.278
I said, “You can cure him, there is a way.”

00:21:49.278 --> 00:21:51.778
So we have a way of giving vibrations

00:21:51.778 --> 00:21:53.808
to that centre of his father

00:21:53.848 --> 00:21:57.068
sitting down in London and
the father was in Scotland.

00:21:58.378 --> 00:22:00.978
After half an hour the
father got up from the bed

00:22:00.978 --> 00:22:03.018
and says, “I don’t know
what has happened.

00:22:03.018 --> 00:22:05.788
I am feeling perfectly alright.”

00:22:05.808 --> 00:22:08.308
So he just laughed
and that’s made him

00:22:08.308 --> 00:22:11.108
understand that there
is a telecommunication

00:22:11.108 --> 00:22:13.608
which we cannot see

00:22:13.608 --> 00:22:16.890
in the universe which works out things.

00:22:16.914 --> 00:22:21.420
But we have to be there to do it,
things and we take it for granted.

00:22:22.110 --> 00:22:24.820
But if you show it to a
villager he cannot believe it

00:22:24.820 --> 00:22:27.320
and when he’ll see it he’ll
say, “It is very fantastic.

00:22:27.320 --> 00:22:28.962
How it is happening?”

00:22:28.972 --> 00:22:31.952
But you have to put it to the
mains otherwise you don’t see it.

00:22:31.972 --> 00:22:37.387
In the same way you are to be put to the
energy mains and so that you start feeling,

00:22:37.387 --> 00:22:44.601
you starting getting the full
answer to your questions.

00:22:44.601 --> 00:22:48.833
But the best part of it that
if you see, say, a television.

00:22:48.853 --> 00:22:52.283
Now you watch some
television, some drama and...

00:22:52.283 --> 00:22:55.043
but you don’t see that they... the

00:22:55.043 --> 00:22:56.803
act … and do something to you.

00:22:56.803 --> 00:23:01.421
But here when you just
project your attention

00:23:01.421 --> 00:23:06.070
to anyone and give it
a little protection,

00:23:06.100 --> 00:23:09.390
you’re amazed that these
vibrations act on that person

00:23:09.420 --> 00:23:12.900
as if the actors come
out of the television

00:23:12.929 --> 00:23:15.769
and try to help you out. It’s so wonderful

00:23:15.800 --> 00:23:17.529
as that and this has happened,

00:23:17.569 --> 00:23:20.069
it is worth trying,
you have those powers.

00:23:20.069 --> 00:23:22.569
You know that our
powers that we know

00:23:22.569 --> 00:23:24.859
as human beings are so limited,

00:23:24.859 --> 00:23:27.359
are so little, like an iceberg

00:23:27.359 --> 00:23:29.859
which is a very wee bit comes out of it,

00:23:29.859 --> 00:23:34.259
the rest is immersed inside. In the
same way our own powers are immersed.

00:23:34.259 --> 00:23:38.239
So the first, the power of
collective consciousness,

00:23:38.249 --> 00:23:40.439
that one gets. And it is to be practised,

00:23:40.439 --> 00:23:42.479
to be understood in its all aspects.

00:23:42.479 --> 00:23:47.379
You become part and parcel
of the Primordial Being.

00:23:47.379 --> 00:23:52.095
If you become part and parcel if my
hand, if supposing my finger is paining

00:23:52.095 --> 00:23:54.595
I rub it off and it is all right,

00:23:54.595 --> 00:23:58.142
I have no obligation to
it, it’s my own finger.

00:23:58.142 --> 00:24:01.505
When everybody is a part
and parcel of your being

00:24:01.505 --> 00:24:04.005
who is the other? If you
are helping somebody

00:24:04.005 --> 00:24:06.505
it’s not, you are
helping yourself because

00:24:06.505 --> 00:24:09.005
it’s you who you are helping.

00:24:09.005 --> 00:24:11.505
So the idea of ego doesn’t come

00:24:11.505 --> 00:24:15.352
that, I have tried to help this man.
I’ve tried to do for this man.

00:24:15.352 --> 00:24:17.852
I’ve done this for him.
None of these ideas!

00:24:17.852 --> 00:24:23.516
And the other one also doesn’t feel
that kind of a burden of obligation.

00:24:23.516 --> 00:24:26.016
So what will you pay? What
will you pay to this finger

00:24:26.016 --> 00:24:28.516
if this hand rubs this?

00:24:29.826 --> 00:24:32.326
It’s just automatic and just your own.

00:24:32.326 --> 00:24:35.369
That is the expansion of your being.

00:24:35.369 --> 00:24:37.659
That’s the expansion of your heart,

00:24:37.659 --> 00:24:43.939
that’s the expansion of your awareness, of
your chitta as we call it, of your attention.

00:24:43.960 --> 00:24:46.629
Attention becomes so much expanded.

00:24:46.629 --> 00:24:51.494
Like my granddaughter, who was
only about four years of age

00:24:51.494 --> 00:24:54.909
and we had taken her to the airport
and she was very busy like this

00:24:54.931 --> 00:24:57.431
so we ask her, “What are you doing?”

00:24:57.431 --> 00:24:59.931
I said. Mother couldn’t
understand. She said,

00:24:59.931 --> 00:25:02.240
“I am trying to tie,
tie up these people.

00:25:02.240 --> 00:25:04.740
They have very scattered brains.

00:25:04.740 --> 00:25:06.710
I’m trying to tie up their brains,

00:25:06.710 --> 00:25:09.520
it’s very scattered brains, all
of them, running up and down.”

00:25:09.520 --> 00:25:12.610
Which is a fact and she was so busy

00:25:12.610 --> 00:25:15.670
and nobody could talk to her because
she said, “I am busy just now.

00:25:15.670 --> 00:25:17.920
Don’t talk to me, I am very busy.”

00:25:17.920 --> 00:25:21.110
And a child like that age
could say all those things

00:25:21.110 --> 00:25:23.819
and the truth is so
evident in their minds.

00:25:23.819 --> 00:25:26.520
Another child of mine who is a grandchild

00:25:26.520 --> 00:25:30.830
and who is another realised soul, all my
four grandchildren are born realised

00:25:30.830 --> 00:25:32.020
and tremendous people,

00:25:32.041 --> 00:25:34.990
so she went to Ladakh once and
there was one lama fellow.

00:25:34.990 --> 00:25:37.490
These lamas are another hawks and

00:25:37.490 --> 00:25:43.935
he was sitting there with a big dress.

00:25:43.961 --> 00:25:45.540
Everybody was touching his feet

00:25:45.543 --> 00:25:48.043
and because, after all,
everybody is touching the feet

00:25:48.043 --> 00:25:50.813
so my daughter and
son-in-law felt embarrassed

00:25:50.813 --> 00:25:52.133
they also went and
touched the feet.

00:25:52.133 --> 00:25:54.633
She couldn’t bear it.
She couldn’t bear that.

00:25:54.633 --> 00:25:57.953
She went and stood before
him with her both hands,

00:25:57.953 --> 00:26:01.493
she locked them at the back
and she stood up and she said,

00:26:01.493 --> 00:26:04.793
“What do you mean? Because
you are wearing this big dress

00:26:04.793 --> 00:26:06.623
– we call it choga, is a big dress –

00:26:06.623 --> 00:26:10.013
and because you have shaved your head you
think you are a realised soul? You are not.

00:26:10.013 --> 00:26:12.976
You have no business to ask
people to touch your feet.”

00:26:12.983 --> 00:26:15.186
Such a little girl like that stood up.

00:26:15.186 --> 00:26:20.796
And once I remember another time
we had a big program in India

00:26:20.816 --> 00:26:24.710
where there is a master who died.

00:26:24.728 --> 00:26:28.100
I think you must have
heard his name also,

00:26:28.106 --> 00:26:33.130
Raman Maharshi, and on his death they
invited me as a chief guest, I was to speak.

00:26:33.130 --> 00:26:35.497
But we had other horrible
people also there;

00:26:35.497 --> 00:26:37.997
somebody from Rama Krishna
ashram and this and that,

00:26:37.997 --> 00:26:41.330
they were sitting. So one fellow
with the Rama Krishna ashram

00:26:41.330 --> 00:26:43.830
was wearing a red robe
and sitting there.

00:26:43.830 --> 00:26:50.750
So one of my son-in-law and
other people were in the group,

00:26:50.750 --> 00:26:54.110
they were sitting on the first
row – the grandchildren,

00:26:54.132 --> 00:26:56.202
and suddenly one of them
got up and he said,

00:26:56.195 --> 00:26:58.695
“Grandmother, please ask this man

00:26:58.695 --> 00:27:02.532
in the maxi to get out. He
is giving all heat to us.”

00:27:03.791 --> 00:27:05.817
And everybody smiled and laughed

00:27:05.817 --> 00:27:08.471
because they were many
Sahaja Yogis there who came

00:27:08.471 --> 00:27:12.511
and they just stand next to me, that
get rid of this fellow with the maxi out

00:27:12.511 --> 00:27:14.141
because he is too much of heat.

00:27:14.141 --> 00:27:16.641
And this fellow thought no
end of himself, you see.

00:27:16.641 --> 00:27:20.691
He thought he was a great man because
he was wearing a maxi in that colour

00:27:20.691 --> 00:27:24.995
and he was giving a big lecture without
understanding what he was talking.

00:27:24.995 --> 00:27:27.355
Just he was going round
and round the bush

00:27:27.355 --> 00:27:30.145
without knowing that he is
not even a realised soul

00:27:30.145 --> 00:27:34.354
and he has no business
to talk about God.

00:27:34.379 --> 00:27:38.575
So the children who are realised souls
are today born in every country,

00:27:38.575 --> 00:27:41.075
I know in Inver, I saw the other day

00:27:41.075 --> 00:27:43.855
going through the market and many
children who are born realised.

00:27:43.855 --> 00:27:46.355
But if the parents are not realised souls

00:27:46.355 --> 00:27:48.855
they will never understand their children

00:27:48.855 --> 00:27:56.601
or their grandchildren and it may be that
you may really destroy their sensitivity.

00:27:56.601 --> 00:27:59.101
So it is important that the elders

00:27:59.101 --> 00:28:01.601
must have a full understanding

00:28:01.601 --> 00:28:03.598
of their children,

00:28:03.598 --> 00:28:07.238
the next generation, which is
going to be very powerful.

00:28:07.238 --> 00:28:09.338
You will see these children
when they willl grow

00:28:09.327 --> 00:28:12.684
they will understand Sahaja
Yoga and Kundalini so well

00:28:12.684 --> 00:28:14.224
that you’ll be amazed.

00:28:14.224 --> 00:28:16.724
For example a child puts his finger

00:28:16.724 --> 00:28:19.904
or a thumb in the mouth people
say it’s something to do with sex

00:28:19.904 --> 00:28:23.364
as Mr. Freud  was
nothing but a sex point.

00:28:23.379 --> 00:28:25.879
He was not a human being
even also, I think.

00:28:25.879 --> 00:28:28.379
So it’s not the case.

00:28:28.379 --> 00:28:33.037
The child, if it is a realised soul,
is pointing it out to the chakras.

00:28:33.947 --> 00:28:36.621
If a child comes here,
he is a realised soul

00:28:36.621 --> 00:28:40.511
and if somebody’s suffering
from a particular trouble,

00:28:40.511 --> 00:28:44.831
he’d immediately put that
particular finger in the mouth.

00:28:44.831 --> 00:28:48.265
Even if you have ten children
and tie up their eyes

00:28:48.265 --> 00:28:50.721
and ask them, “What’s
wrong with this fellow?”

00:28:50.735 --> 00:28:53.441
they’ll put out one finger or two fingers,

00:28:53.441 --> 00:28:55.791
whatever are burning.

00:28:55.791 --> 00:29:00.881
Because it is such a actual
experience of that person’s chakras

00:29:00.881 --> 00:29:04.261
and they will immediately
say these two are burning

00:29:04.261 --> 00:29:05.731
or these three are burning

00:29:05.765 --> 00:29:08.265
and all of them will
say the same thing.

00:29:08.995 --> 00:29:14.531
So it is the knowledge of your
own central nervous system.

00:29:14.531 --> 00:29:18.635
It is not a knowledge which
is given to you in your brain

00:29:18.665 --> 00:29:21.165
or just to

00:29:21.165 --> 00:29:23.804
be pushed into your ideas,

00:29:23.804 --> 00:29:27.614
it’s a fact, factual
thing that you know.

00:29:27.622 --> 00:29:31.201
Like you all know this is wood,

00:29:31.212 --> 00:29:33.712
all know this is wood, made of wood.

00:29:33.712 --> 00:29:36.722
In the same way you
will know the truth

00:29:36.722 --> 00:29:39.222
because you become absolutely

00:29:39.222 --> 00:29:41.722
the absolute,

00:29:42.392 --> 00:29:45.370
the absolute. You know the absolute,

00:29:45.370 --> 00:29:49.100
there is no more any relative world left,

00:29:49.100 --> 00:29:52.030
you don’t live in the relative world.

00:29:52.060 --> 00:29:54.560
This may be good and
that may be good.

00:29:54.560 --> 00:29:57.510
This could be alright or
that could be alright.

00:29:57.510 --> 00:30:00.010
That doesn’t come. Whatever is good

00:30:00.010 --> 00:30:03.358
is good, whatever is bad is bad.

00:30:03.378 --> 00:30:06.028
You don’t have to even
think of temptations,

00:30:06.028 --> 00:30:08.528
your temptations drop out very fast.

00:30:08.528 --> 00:30:12.027
All your habits drop out very fast.

00:30:12.053 --> 00:30:14.157
For example, Brian himself

00:30:14.157 --> 00:30:16.657
who spoke first of here

00:30:16.657 --> 00:30:19.157
was a smoker and

00:30:19.157 --> 00:30:22.998
used to smoke a lot and he had a
very bad trouble with the smoking.

00:30:23.022 --> 00:30:25.522
And next day he dropped the smoking,

00:30:25.522 --> 00:30:28.496
next day, you won’t believe,
he dropped his smoking.

00:30:28.496 --> 00:30:30.732
He had other problem
that he had crutches

00:30:30.739 --> 00:30:32.392
and  he just could not walk

00:30:32.384 --> 00:30:34.884
even an inch without the crutches,

00:30:34.884 --> 00:30:37.384
hanging onto the crutches like that,

00:30:37.384 --> 00:30:40.594
only with the crutches, he
could not move his legs at all.

00:30:40.594 --> 00:30:43.832
Today he is standing on his legs
and you see he is walking.

00:30:43.847 --> 00:30:45.632
This I did not do anything.

00:30:45.651 --> 00:30:50.102
It just worked through
the power of your Self.

00:30:50.102 --> 00:30:52.602
Your Self, itself, cures you

00:30:52.602 --> 00:30:54.672
and gives you powers to cure others.

00:30:54.672 --> 00:30:57.402
But in the beginning you
don’t have faith in yourself.

00:30:57.402 --> 00:31:00.062
Even If I say that you can cure others

00:31:00.062 --> 00:31:02.562
you will not cure. This is a big problem

00:31:02.562 --> 00:31:05.585
that one doesn’t assume

00:31:05.602 --> 00:31:08.545
the powers that they have,
doesn’t believe in them.

00:31:08.545 --> 00:31:11.641
Once I was travelling by a ship

00:31:11.675 --> 00:31:15.161
and there was the captain
who got his Realisation

00:31:15.185 --> 00:31:18.531
and they told me that there is one fellow

00:31:18.531 --> 00:31:22.602
who has got pneumonia because he
entered into the freezing room,

00:31:22.608 --> 00:31:25.412
they have a freezer, just like a room.

00:31:25.448 --> 00:31:29.592
And he entered into it suddenly so he
got pneumonia and he was gasping and

00:31:29.590 --> 00:31:32.090
they had to send an SOS
to get some doctor.

00:31:32.090 --> 00:31:35.640
So I told the captain
I can go and cure him.

00:31:35.640 --> 00:31:38.140
He said, “No, Mother, why should
you go?” After all, you see,

00:31:38.140 --> 00:31:40.640
I was the wife of the.., you see,  owners

00:31:40.640 --> 00:31:43.140
and all that so they
found it was too much

00:31:43.140 --> 00:31:45.640
for me to go down four,  five stories

00:31:45.640 --> 00:31:48.380
to the freezing room

00:31:48.420 --> 00:31:50.920
to safe this fellow. So
I said, “Alright. Captain,

00:31:50.920 --> 00:31:52.650
you are a realised soul,
why don’t you do it?

00:31:52.650 --> 00:31:55.150
A simple thing, simple
method I’ll tell you

00:31:55.150 --> 00:31:58.091
and he’ll be alright.”
He said, “How can I?

00:31:58.091 --> 00:32:01.890
I am not … I am just … Yesterday
only I got my Realisation,

00:32:01.935 --> 00:32:03.270
how can I?”

00:32:03.302 --> 00:32:05.910
I said, “Alright. Now he is
going to die if you don’t do it.

00:32:05.910 --> 00:32:09.529
So please try, if it doesn’t
work out I’ll come down.”

00:32:09.556 --> 00:32:12.696
So he went down, out of that
compassion he went down.

00:32:12.726 --> 00:32:15.226
And he came up laughing,
“Mother, I’ve cured him.

00:32:15.226 --> 00:32:16.830
He’s alright.”

00:32:16.829 --> 00:32:19.329
I said, “Now, please believe that

00:32:19.329 --> 00:32:21.410
you are now a yogi,

00:32:21.420 --> 00:32:22.800
you are a realised soul.”

00:32:22.788 --> 00:32:24.600
We do not believe in ourselves.

00:32:24.600 --> 00:32:27.100
We doubt ourselves more
than anybody else.

00:32:27.100 --> 00:32:29.600
And this is the biggest problem

00:32:29.600 --> 00:32:32.123
that we want to have a guru
because we think, “Alright.

00:32:32.140 --> 00:32:34.640
We’ll believe in this
person. He goes to hell,

00:32:34.640 --> 00:32:37.788
we go to hell with him.” If he goes to
heaven we’ll go to heaven with him.

00:32:37.788 --> 00:32:40.680
Pay some money and have
somebody on whom we can rely.

00:32:40.680 --> 00:32:42.480
But now rely upon yourself.

00:32:42.480 --> 00:32:44.980
Stand on your own feet

00:32:45.820 --> 00:32:48.880
because you are the enlightened ones.

00:32:48.880 --> 00:32:53.530
You are the Buddhas – you are the
ones who have achieved enlightenment.

00:32:53.529 --> 00:32:55.469
Don’t depend on anybody else,

00:32:55.469 --> 00:33:00.329
there is no guru needed, you yourself can
know through vibrations what has to be done.

00:33:00.329 --> 00:33:03.737
Like one gentleman who got his Realisation,

00:33:03.772 --> 00:33:05.207
he had no job.

00:33:05.221 --> 00:33:06.737
So he said, “Mother,
what should I do?”

00:33:06.737 --> 00:33:09.087
I said, “Why don’t you become
an interior decorator?”

00:33:09.087 --> 00:33:10.337
He was quite surprised,

00:33:10.337 --> 00:33:13.328
he said, “Mother, I’ve done
economics but I’ve never done this.

00:33:13.328 --> 00:33:15.828
I don’t know a wood from
another wood. What am I to do?”

00:33:15.828 --> 00:33:18.328
I said, “Just see vibrations and do it.”

00:33:18.328 --> 00:33:20.828
And he became a very rich man,

00:33:20.828 --> 00:33:23.328
he’ll be coming now to Australia

00:33:23.328 --> 00:33:24.946
to join us in Sydney.

00:33:24.946 --> 00:33:27.446
But this is what happens that once

00:33:27.446 --> 00:33:29.946
you have vibrations
immediately you know

00:33:29.946 --> 00:33:31.730
what is to be done,

00:33:31.730 --> 00:33:34.660
what will create

00:33:34.680 --> 00:33:37.944
the right thing for you.

00:33:37.950 --> 00:33:40.450
This is absolutely

00:33:40.450 --> 00:33:43.191
easy to do if you assume your powers.

00:33:43.191 --> 00:33:46.110
But if you are diffident,
“Oh, how can I do it?

00:33:46.120 --> 00:33:48.620
It’s better Mother does it
or somebody else does it.”

00:33:48.620 --> 00:33:51.290
then it doesn’t work out.
But if you say, “Alright.

00:33:51.290 --> 00:33:53.519
I am a yogi and I can do it.”

00:33:53.519 --> 00:33:56.019
You see these gurus are
not even realised souls.

00:33:56.019 --> 00:33:58.069
Some of them are coming from jail,

00:33:58.069 --> 00:34:00.699
they have no bona fides,
they are horrid people

00:34:00.699 --> 00:34:03.199
and imagine what organisations
they have had built,

00:34:03.199 --> 00:34:06.374
thousands and thousands of
people, just like this.

00:34:06.374 --> 00:34:08.874
A servant coming out of some place

00:34:08.874 --> 00:34:11.374
becomes a big guru in
Germany or somewhere,

00:34:11.374 --> 00:34:13.364
owns 59 Rolls-Royces.

00:34:13.364 --> 00:34:14.974
What do you say to such a thing?

00:34:14.974 --> 00:34:17.224
Because they are bumptious.

00:34:17.224 --> 00:34:19.724
You are not to be bumptious but believe

00:34:19.724 --> 00:34:22.224
that now you have got your powers.

00:34:22.224 --> 00:34:24.724
And when you have
your powers use them

00:34:24.724 --> 00:34:28.115
because that’s the greatest joy.

00:34:28.115 --> 00:34:31.555
I mean, you see your
compassion working it out

00:34:31.555 --> 00:34:33.745
when you see people
get their Realisation.

00:34:33.746 --> 00:34:36.246
Every Realisation you feel as if you have

00:34:36.246 --> 00:34:39.455
made one flower into a fruit.

00:34:39.465 --> 00:34:41.965
And you feel so surprised first

00:34:41.966 --> 00:34:44.466
at yourself and then at the divine Grace

00:34:44.466 --> 00:34:46.966
that he has made you so great and

00:34:46.966 --> 00:34:49.466
you have been not aware of it,

00:34:49.466 --> 00:34:51.966
that you can do living work.

00:34:51.986 --> 00:34:54.842
These vibrations when
given to the plants,

00:34:54.852 --> 00:34:58.312
supposing a plant is
dying. Like in

00:34:58.322 --> 00:35:00.993
Geneva we have a very
beautiful ashram

00:35:00.993 --> 00:35:04.223
where they had a
tree which was dying

00:35:04.250 --> 00:35:08.297
and they were about to cut it out. They
said, “Let’s try the vibrations on it.”

00:35:08.319 --> 00:35:10.819
And when I went there the tree was lush,

00:35:10.819 --> 00:35:13.319
beautiful, but best was they

00:35:13.319 --> 00:35:17.910
had such huge big, big
cherries for me to eat.

00:35:17.920 --> 00:35:20.778
And this was the first time, they
said, when we gave vibrations

00:35:20.778 --> 00:35:23.360
and such big cherries
came and so many that

00:35:23.360 --> 00:35:25.860
there were at least five
hundred people all together.

00:35:25.860 --> 00:35:28.360
We all ate and ate and ate and

00:35:28.360 --> 00:35:31.738
it would not finish. And I like cherries

00:35:31.778 --> 00:35:34.278
and they said, “Mother, you
better take it with you

00:35:34.278 --> 00:35:36.178
to England.” I said,
“That’s too much now.”

00:35:36.178 --> 00:35:37.868
They said, “Still they
are not going to finish

00:35:37.890 --> 00:35:41.238
so better take some of
them with you to England.”

00:35:41.245 --> 00:35:44.718
Especially Switzerland is a place where
they don’t grow very big cherries

00:35:44.750 --> 00:35:46.208
but such big big cherries,

00:35:46.208 --> 00:35:50.535
you see, and some cherries that I’ll say that
I’ve never seen such nice and tasty cherries.

00:35:50.535 --> 00:35:54.348
I’ve told you if you give
these vibrations to anything,

00:35:54.364 --> 00:35:57.574
like a vegetable, plant

00:35:57.583 --> 00:36:03.524
or any crop, the crops
multiply in its production.

00:36:03.549 --> 00:36:06.049
Not only that but the crops

00:36:06.049 --> 00:36:08.449
are not hybrid crops,

00:36:08.449 --> 00:36:11.869
without giving any fertilizer

00:36:11.909 --> 00:36:15.767
or giving any hybrid....using
the hybrid thing,

00:36:15.767 --> 00:36:19.589
you can use just the ordinary

00:36:19.589 --> 00:36:22.089
crops... seeds and
can work it out.

00:36:22.089 --> 00:36:24.909
Now what has happened: by the
use of these ordinary seeds,

00:36:24.909 --> 00:36:27.409
the seeds have become weak
and that’s why we have

00:36:27.449 --> 00:36:32.139
to have hybrid things,
artificially strengthened seeds.

00:36:32.159 --> 00:36:34.779
But when you give
vibrations to these crops

00:36:34.779 --> 00:36:37.519
what happens – that these crops

00:36:37.519 --> 00:36:40.019
get the vital energy within themselves

00:36:40.019 --> 00:36:42.199
and they become like original ones.

00:36:42.199 --> 00:36:47.952
And they start producing
tremendous amount of grains.

00:36:47.959 --> 00:36:50.019
There is a university
in Rahuri where people

00:36:50.019 --> 00:36:54.781
have experimented in
the agriculture field.

00:36:54.800 --> 00:36:59.031
I was told that New Zealand
is an agricultural land.

00:36:59.038 --> 00:37:01.538
We have not to play into the hands

00:37:01.538 --> 00:37:05.073
of any big organizations
who are selling us

00:37:05.098 --> 00:37:07.598
these hybrid seeds
which cannot be used

00:37:07.598 --> 00:37:11.843
if the plant even gives
you any amount of seeds we

00:37:11.843 --> 00:37:14.343
cannot use them for replanting.

00:37:14.343 --> 00:37:16.731
But the seeds which are natural

00:37:16.731 --> 00:37:19.921
if you vibrate them and
put them in the soil

00:37:19.949 --> 00:37:22.449
you’ll be surprised you’ll get sometimes

00:37:22.449 --> 00:37:26.552
the results are at least ten times more.

00:37:26.567 --> 00:37:29.067
One gentleman in
Austria has experimented

00:37:29.067 --> 00:37:32.211
with that and he has shown
pictures and photographs

00:37:32.241 --> 00:37:34.741
and we have sent them to India.

00:37:34.741 --> 00:37:38.162
India is a better country
to understand Sahaja Yoga

00:37:38.162 --> 00:37:40.072
because even the
government understands,

00:37:40.072 --> 00:37:44.362
even the public understands and
everybody is helping us very much.

00:37:44.362 --> 00:37:46.862
In Delhi university we have got

00:37:46.862 --> 00:37:50.005
a PhD,

00:37:50.005 --> 00:37:52.635
after doing MBBS they have to do PhD

00:37:52.635 --> 00:37:55.009
a doctorate in Sahaja Yoga.

00:37:55.009 --> 00:37:57.509
Even in London we have
got in Cambridge

00:37:57.509 --> 00:38:00.335
a subject called a PSD in Sahaja Yoga.

00:38:00.335 --> 00:38:02.835
There is one also, thanks to

00:38:02.835 --> 00:38:06.355
some Americans, they’ve first
that in American university,

00:38:06.355 --> 00:38:08.715
they have also accepted in New York.

00:38:08.715 --> 00:38:11.975
So you can imagine how far it has gone

00:38:12.008 --> 00:38:17.356
in some places as far as the scientific
understanding of Sahaja Yoga is concerned.

00:38:17.356 --> 00:38:21.468
But the basics have to be first understood.

00:38:21.490 --> 00:38:25.570
If you understand the basic
that it is the compassion of God

00:38:25.570 --> 00:38:30.481
that works it out and that we
have to be compassionate people.

00:38:30.502 --> 00:38:33.962
I will tell you, as you’ve
seen today Dr Reeves,

00:38:33.962 --> 00:38:36.462
he was a very influential man,

00:38:36.462 --> 00:38:38.782
he’s done his PhDs in three subjects

00:38:38.782 --> 00:38:41.282
and he is also a Doctor
and he was a diplomat, and

00:38:41.282 --> 00:38:43.782
this and that, and when he
came to me he was riding

00:38:43.782 --> 00:38:46.282
a very high horse but

00:38:46.282 --> 00:38:49.487
after Realisation he is so changed,

00:38:49.505 --> 00:38:51.327
he’s become such a beautiful person.

00:38:51.333 --> 00:38:53.833
He is so changed, all his temperament,

00:38:53.833 --> 00:38:56.973
and everything changed, he
is such a nice person now

00:38:56.985 --> 00:38:59.783
that people can’t believe he is the same.

00:38:59.805 --> 00:39:01.413
You change in such a way

00:39:01.413 --> 00:39:05.633
that you become a personality
which is magnetic and loving,

00:39:05.654 --> 00:39:08.474
and affectionate, patient, tolerant

00:39:08.504 --> 00:39:10.564
and peaceful personality.

00:39:10.564 --> 00:39:13.064
Now also we are having some schools,

00:39:13.064 --> 00:39:15.564
even in Australia we have
a school for children,

00:39:15.564 --> 00:39:18.064
and the report of the school was thus

00:39:18.064 --> 00:39:21.657
that the children are extremely peaceful,

00:39:21.684 --> 00:39:24.857
extremely obedient and very disciplined.

00:39:24.887 --> 00:39:27.587
They will not take to drugs, they
will not take to wrong things,

00:39:27.587 --> 00:39:29.213
they will  not do thieving,

00:39:29.222 --> 00:39:31.503
we don’t have to tell them,
they have no temptations,

00:39:31.503 --> 00:39:34.003
they are satisfied souls, they
are not going to nag you,

00:39:34.003 --> 00:39:35.423
they are not going to bother you.

00:39:35.423 --> 00:39:38.463
They are going to look after you
and they are going to respect.

00:39:39.483 --> 00:39:41.983
This is what comes out
of Sahaja Yoga schools.

00:39:41.983 --> 00:39:44.483
We are having schools
even in Switzerland

00:39:44.483 --> 00:39:46.983
and everywhere we have
schools for such children

00:39:46.983 --> 00:39:49.621
and it is amazing how the children are.

00:39:49.621 --> 00:39:52.291
They are beautiful children,
extremely beautiful.

00:39:52.291 --> 00:39:54.791
As the human beings
become beautiful

00:39:54.791 --> 00:39:57.441
in their own glory they
rise the children also

00:39:57.441 --> 00:40:00.701
and children really are remarkable,

00:40:00.701 --> 00:40:03.201
remarkable people. If you
see them you’ll be amazed.

00:40:03.201 --> 00:40:05.701
Everyone you’ll find is the same and talks

00:40:05.701 --> 00:40:08.201
like some great saint like Kabira

00:40:08.201 --> 00:40:10.426
or Nanaka, they talk so big.

00:40:10.426 --> 00:40:12.926
We cannot understand how
these little, little things

00:40:12.926 --> 00:40:14.054
have so much of sense.

00:40:14.116 --> 00:40:16.616
For example, one more
thing I’ll tell you

00:40:16.616 --> 00:40:19.304
about my grandchild
which was the youngest,

00:40:19.304 --> 00:40:21.804
she was about three years of age and

00:40:21.804 --> 00:40:26.117
she told her mother, “Mother, you
are now practising homoeopathy,

00:40:26.117 --> 00:40:28.617
you were born in allopathy,

00:40:28.617 --> 00:40:30.837
then you’re practising homoeopathy,

00:40:30.837 --> 00:40:35.047
then you’ll practice jumbopathy,
then will be cambopathy.

00:40:35.098 --> 00:40:37.598
But I will never

00:40:37.598 --> 00:40:40.797
do all these things
because I was born in God

00:40:40.810 --> 00:40:44.097
and God will cure me
and I live in God.”

00:40:44.131 --> 00:40:48.677
So she said ,"Why not you...". The mother
said, “Why not, you may also change.”

00:40:48.677 --> 00:40:51.577
She said, “How can I?
Because God never changes.”

00:40:53.477 --> 00:40:58.101
What a fundamental understanding

00:40:58.121 --> 00:41:01.151
about life and this is what happens.

00:41:01.161 --> 00:41:03.661
And even an ordinary

00:41:03.661 --> 00:41:06.721
fisherman you meet who is a realised soul,

00:41:06.773 --> 00:41:09.273
if you meet an ordinary bullock cart driver ….

00:41:09.273 --> 00:41:12.410
Once I was going with a bullock
cart, you all know a bullock cart,

00:41:12.443 --> 00:41:14.943
and he was talking I felt this is some

00:41:14.943 --> 00:41:19.080
great Markandeya or
some great William Blake

00:41:19.080 --> 00:41:22.851
is talking to me, such
beautiful things he was saying.

00:41:22.878 --> 00:41:25.568
So I said, “How do you
know all these things?

00:41:25.568 --> 00:41:28.538
You’ve never been to any
university.” He said, “Why?

00:41:28.558 --> 00:41:31.878
I know because I know God,

00:41:31.908 --> 00:41:34.408
because it is all in my brain,

00:41:34.408 --> 00:41:35.758
it all comes to me.”

00:41:35.758 --> 00:41:38.258
So all the subtler things that

00:41:38.258 --> 00:41:40.758
are in your brain come to light

00:41:40.758 --> 00:41:44.368
and you become really a
very subtle personality

00:41:45.408 --> 00:41:47.468
but first of all you
must assume the power.

00:41:47.472 --> 00:41:49.618
So you become collectively conscious,

00:41:49.649 --> 00:41:52.149
your attention becomes
collectively conscious.

00:41:52.149 --> 00:41:54.649
Then you become the truth.

00:41:54.649 --> 00:41:57.149
Because you know the truth
you become the truth.

00:41:57.149 --> 00:41:59.649
You cannot tolerate anything
that is not the truth.

00:41:59.649 --> 00:42:03.280
All falsehood drops out,
all corruption drops out,

00:42:03.303 --> 00:42:06.848
all kinds of funny things we
do out of insecurity drop out,

00:42:06.855 --> 00:42:08.568
our health improves.

00:42:08.576 --> 00:42:11.076
So what happens to us: that we

00:42:11.076 --> 00:42:13.576
become a personality

00:42:13.576 --> 00:42:16.076
who has got the truth within but

00:42:16.076 --> 00:42:18.576
we are very humble. We
are extremely humble,

00:42:18.576 --> 00:42:21.076
we do not want to push people into it,

00:42:21.076 --> 00:42:23.576
we do not want to force
them anything. But we see

00:42:23.576 --> 00:42:26.223
the truth clearly, as a witness
we know this is the truth

00:42:26.223 --> 00:42:30.473
and nothing, nothing can disturb us.

00:42:31.402 --> 00:42:33.902
As in the life of Christ, you see,

00:42:33.902 --> 00:42:36.402
he saw a prostitute being stoned. Now

00:42:36.402 --> 00:42:41.118
Christ, a saint, a great divine personality,

00:42:41.134 --> 00:42:43.848
had nothing to do with a
prostitute, they’ve nothing to do.

00:42:43.848 --> 00:42:46.348
But when he saw a
prostitute being stoned

00:42:46.348 --> 00:42:48.474
he stood up with the truth,

00:42:48.474 --> 00:42:50.564
in his strength he
stands up and he says,

00:42:50.587 --> 00:42:53.904
“Those who have not sinned
can throw a stone at me.”

00:42:54.823 --> 00:42:57.013
and nobody did that.

00:42:57.013 --> 00:43:00.803
Because he knew the truth, they
could see the strength of truth.

00:43:00.803 --> 00:43:03.303
All great men of the world have used

00:43:03.303 --> 00:43:05.803
this strength of truth in their lives.

00:43:05.803 --> 00:43:08.183
Most of them have been realised souls.

00:43:08.183 --> 00:43:11.453
I can tell you so many names: like
Abraham Lincoln was a realised soul,

00:43:12.503 --> 00:43:14.283
Mozart was a realised soul,

00:43:14.304 --> 00:43:17.257
so many people you can know
that they were a realised soul

00:43:17.257 --> 00:43:19.364
though we do not do know that
they were realised souls.

00:43:19.384 --> 00:43:22.154
Like our Lord Mountbatten
was a realised soul,

00:43:22.154 --> 00:43:24.654
Barbara Cartland is a realised soul.

00:43:24.654 --> 00:43:27.851
All these people are realised souls,

00:43:27.851 --> 00:43:30.534
they know they are realized souls
but they don’t want to talk about it

00:43:30.534 --> 00:43:32.904
because they think that
if we say anything

00:43:32.904 --> 00:43:36.048
people will think we are trying
to push our ways onto them.

00:43:36.048 --> 00:43:38.954
They enjoy their Realisation.

00:43:38.998 --> 00:43:41.498
But Realisation is no more a private thing,

00:43:41.498 --> 00:43:43.998
it is no more a private thing, it is

00:43:43.998 --> 00:43:45.825
a public thing.

00:43:45.846 --> 00:43:49.825
It has to go to the society,
it has to do good to others,

00:43:49.835 --> 00:43:52.335
it has to help others;
it has not to just

00:43:52.335 --> 00:43:56.105
stick onto your goodness that now
you have a good place to live in,

00:43:56.133 --> 00:43:58.335
you have got beautiful
children and a wife

00:43:58.335 --> 00:44:00.835
so now you be comfortable.
No, you will not.

00:44:00.835 --> 00:44:03.335
Like the lady today
interviewed asked me,

00:44:03.335 --> 00:44:05.835
“You have such a nice
house, such a nice husband,

00:44:05.835 --> 00:44:08.335
you are so comfortable so
why are you travelling?”

00:44:08.335 --> 00:44:10.724
I said, “First of all, my
husband has no objection.

00:44:10.724 --> 00:44:14.214
He thinks that this is the only
way the world can be transformed.

00:44:14.214 --> 00:44:16.714
Though he is so highly placed in life

00:44:16.714 --> 00:44:19.214
he is convinced no use
having organisations

00:44:19.214 --> 00:44:21.844
in the name of United
Nations and all that,

00:44:21.844 --> 00:44:23.844
they are not united.”

00:44:23.854 --> 00:44:26.124
But unless and until the Spirit

00:44:26.124 --> 00:44:28.234
dawns upon you, you cannot be united.

00:44:28.234 --> 00:44:30.734
And this is what he has
realised and he says

00:44:30.734 --> 00:44:33.234
that, “It’s alright if you have to
travel I have nothing to say.”

00:44:33.234 --> 00:44:35.410
because he himself travels so much.

00:44:35.410 --> 00:44:37.910
He has no objection to do
that, he understands me

00:44:37.910 --> 00:44:40.410
because he has seen the
transformation taking place

00:44:40.410 --> 00:44:43.433
so well. When I was just married he said,

00:44:43.433 --> 00:44:46.887
“I believe, I know that you
are something very different

00:44:46.887 --> 00:44:49.833
we call it Auliya to a realised
soul. "You are an Auliya

00:44:49.857 --> 00:44:52.357
 and you are not bothered

00:44:52.357 --> 00:44:54.547
about anything because
you are like that.

00:44:54.547 --> 00:44:57.047
But I can’t believe that
you can transform others

00:44:57.047 --> 00:44:59.297
to your state, you
cannot.” But now he says,

00:44:59.297 --> 00:45:02.617
“I cannot be dishonest anymore,
I see the transformation.

00:45:02.617 --> 00:45:06.297
People have given up all their bad habits,
have become such beautiful people.”

00:45:06.297 --> 00:45:08.797
If you see their faces, they’re shining

00:45:08.797 --> 00:45:11.699
like lotuses.

00:45:11.739 --> 00:45:14.239
You see them at the
airport, they stand out

00:45:14.239 --> 00:45:16.739
by their beautiful behaviour,

00:45:16.739 --> 00:45:19.849
the decorum, the
decency that they have.

00:45:19.859 --> 00:45:22.359
It is such a beautiful life they are leading.

00:45:22.359 --> 00:45:24.859
I want all of you to
lead that beautiful life.

00:45:24.859 --> 00:45:27.219
But do not keep it for your private use,

00:45:27.219 --> 00:45:29.409
do not keep it only
for your relations,

00:45:29.410 --> 00:45:32.129
for your own family but give it to others.

00:45:32.160 --> 00:45:34.979
Unless and until you
gave it has no meaning.

00:45:35.870 --> 00:45:38.370
Now the third thing that happens

00:45:38.370 --> 00:45:41.067
to a human being as
Self-realisation comes in:

00:45:41.067 --> 00:45:45.957
that he becomes
the enjoyer of joy.

00:45:45.977 --> 00:45:48.697
We have no idea of joy.

00:45:48.755 --> 00:45:51.255
To us if our ego is pampered,

00:45:51.255 --> 00:45:53.755
if somebody is nice to us,
they give us nice things

00:45:53.755 --> 00:45:56.689
or something, our ego is
pampered if it is happening.

00:45:56.705 --> 00:45:59.019
If somebody insults us we feel unhappy.

00:45:59.019 --> 00:46:02.038
But the state of joy has no duality.

00:46:02.038 --> 00:46:06.159
When you do all these things you are
either on the ego or on the superego,

00:46:06.159 --> 00:46:08.659
moving from one to another. But when

00:46:08.659 --> 00:46:11.845
you are in joy you are just
witnessing the whole thing,

00:46:11.845 --> 00:46:15.549
the whole thing just
works as a formless joy.

00:46:15.570 --> 00:46:18.070
But that formless joy has a feeling

00:46:18.070 --> 00:46:20.694
within yourself also, you
get a feeling of that joy

00:46:20.694 --> 00:46:23.194
and that feeling sometimes I

00:46:23.194 --> 00:46:26.270
describe it as if something very soothing

00:46:26.305 --> 00:46:30.204
comes over you like Grace and you
are filled with that soothing.

00:46:30.204 --> 00:46:34.955
The whole being becomes soothed,
you feel extremely joyous.

00:46:34.977 --> 00:46:38.697
You cannot explain

00:46:38.727 --> 00:46:39.927
a feeling.

00:46:39.933 --> 00:46:42.433
Kabira said, “Now I’ve become

00:46:42.433 --> 00:46:45.387
intoxicated with joy, what can I talk,

00:46:45.423 --> 00:46:47.923
how can I talk!” You
see a person who cannot

00:46:47.923 --> 00:46:50.423
talk when he is

00:46:50.423 --> 00:46:53.657
eating the nectar of love,
how can you talk about it.

00:46:53.657 --> 00:46:56.707
You better eat and enjoy
because you must taste it.

00:46:56.707 --> 00:46:59.207
How can I tell you what
is this taste unless

00:46:59.207 --> 00:47:01.119
and until you have this taste.

00:47:01.119 --> 00:47:03.619
Supposing I talk to you about something

00:47:03.619 --> 00:47:06.119
you have never seen,
how will you know?

00:47:06.119 --> 00:47:08.619
So better see it
yourself. In the same way

00:47:08.619 --> 00:47:12.510
everybody who
experiences it will know

00:47:12.534 --> 00:47:15.034
that it is

00:47:15.048 --> 00:47:17.548
a thing of joy which cannot be explained.

00:47:17.548 --> 00:47:19.694
You become a peaceful person,

00:47:19.694 --> 00:47:22.194
you become a joyous person and for the

00:47:22.194 --> 00:47:27.305
first time you start enjoying another
personality in its pure form.

00:47:27.995 --> 00:47:30.994
Normally we enjoy another personality,

00:47:30.994 --> 00:47:32.734
we think we enjoy,

00:47:32.744 --> 00:47:35.244
but we are happy with
another person because

00:47:35.244 --> 00:47:37.744
we have some lust or
greed, or some sort

00:47:37.744 --> 00:47:40.244
of a relationship with that person,

00:47:40.244 --> 00:47:45.713
or some sort of a thought, that you do
not feel the inner being of that person.

00:47:45.713 --> 00:47:47.894
But when you feel that subtle being

00:47:47.894 --> 00:47:52.297
you are so full of joy that you
do not know what is happening,

00:47:52.297 --> 00:47:53.604
how you are feeling.

00:47:53.618 --> 00:47:56.814
But for that you have to
develop that sensitivity.

00:47:56.832 --> 00:47:59.332
Once I was in Calcutta

00:47:59.332 --> 00:48:01.688
and we had gone and
stayed in a hotel;

00:48:01.688 --> 00:48:04.378
and normally I don’t like to
stay in a hotel but the owner

00:48:04.378 --> 00:48:06.878
was a Sahaja Yogi so I stayed there.

00:48:06.878 --> 00:48:09.378
And the owner came to see me

00:48:09.378 --> 00:48:11.655
and he was just touching my feet

00:48:11.655 --> 00:48:14.155
because in India the custom is
that you must touch the feet

00:48:14.155 --> 00:48:17.238
of a saint and of your
guru. So he touched my feet

00:48:17.253 --> 00:48:20.418
and there were three, four other
Sahaja Yogis staying in other rooms.

00:48:20.418 --> 00:48:23.510
They suddenly felt
tremendous joy on their

00:48:23.510 --> 00:48:26.010
Sahasrara and they started

00:48:26.010 --> 00:48:28.600
off to my room, all of
them from different rooms.

00:48:28.600 --> 00:48:31.310
They just came rushing, “What’s
happening, Mother?”  I said, “Why?”

00:48:31.310 --> 00:48:34.610
“We felt tremendous joy.”
I said, “See this one.”

00:48:34.610 --> 00:48:37.110
So they put their hands to him, “Aaahh”

00:48:37.110 --> 00:48:40.810
as if some great fragrance
of beauty is coming on them

00:48:40.810 --> 00:48:43.310
and when they felt, “Aaaahhaaa,
what is happening?

00:48:43.310 --> 00:48:47.790
I said, “Look at that, you
are also the same type.”

00:48:48.980 --> 00:48:51.480
And then they started
enjoying each other.

00:48:51.480 --> 00:48:53.980
So there is no quarrel,
there is no fighting,

00:48:53.980 --> 00:48:55.870
there is no harsh words, nothing.

00:48:55.870 --> 00:49:00.510
You even don’t talk much but you are
enjoying each other in pure love,

00:49:00.510 --> 00:49:03.790
not with any lust, greed
or any relationship,

00:49:03.828 --> 00:49:08.357
this funny relationships that we have developed.

00:49:08.367 --> 00:49:11.427
Two persons cannot genuinely love,

00:49:11.457 --> 00:49:12.997
that all finishes off.

00:49:13.037 --> 00:49:15.537
Thousands of them
love each other in

00:49:15.537 --> 00:49:18.867
such a way that it is ...

00:49:18.887 --> 00:49:22.287
it is really impossible to
believe how things happen.

00:49:22.287 --> 00:49:25.677
There is a Muslim boy who was in Algeria.

00:49:25.677 --> 00:49:28.397
And in Algeria the fundamentalists
started taking over

00:49:28.397 --> 00:49:30.320
and the boys got very much worried

00:49:30.336 --> 00:49:33.950
and they all become communists because they
thought this God business is horrible,

00:49:33.950 --> 00:49:39.284
these fundamentalists are ruining
Iran, Iraq and we’ll be also ruined.

00:49:39.304 --> 00:49:43.434
So they became all communists, about
five hundred of them, educated boys.

00:49:43.482 --> 00:49:47.186
And this one was an engineer,
aeronautical engineer, very intelligent.

00:49:47.186 --> 00:49:50.462
He came to London and some how or
other he came to Sahaja Yoga.

00:49:50.482 --> 00:49:53.086
He got his Realisation
and then he went and

00:49:53.086 --> 00:49:56.418
told them that no, there is God,

00:49:56.416 --> 00:49:59.648
no doubt, we have to find
him within ourselves.

00:49:59.660 --> 00:50:02.035
He gave Realisation to
all five hundred of them

00:50:02.035 --> 00:50:04.240
and now in Algeria
which is a Muslim country

00:50:04.240 --> 00:50:07.650
we have many Sahaja Yogis, even
some barristers are Sahaja Yogis,

00:50:07.650 --> 00:50:11.138
so many are there because they are
people of very sharp intelligence.

00:50:11.138 --> 00:50:13.830
I find they have that pure intelligence

00:50:13.830 --> 00:50:15.770
in their heads to see the point,

00:50:15.770 --> 00:50:17.220
that this is what it is.

00:50:17.220 --> 00:50:19.720
And now this boy when he went

00:50:19.720 --> 00:50:22.700
and told them about
this they were amazed

00:50:22.700 --> 00:50:25.640
because they said that
this is within ourselves

00:50:25.640 --> 00:50:28.140
and a one boy can do
that for five hundred so

00:50:28.140 --> 00:50:30.910
why not we go across and do it to others.

00:50:30.910 --> 00:50:34.100
And that’s how they are
spreading Sahaja Yoga everywhere.

00:50:34.100 --> 00:50:36.600
So like one seed which is enlightened

00:50:36.600 --> 00:50:39.220
can know

00:50:39.240 --> 00:50:41.740
and give a big tree, in the same way

00:50:41.740 --> 00:50:44.240
one person can give Realisation

00:50:44.240 --> 00:50:46.919
to many people, thousands.

00:50:46.919 --> 00:50:50.059
And you all have to only
know your own powers.

00:50:50.059 --> 00:50:52.689
Do not limit it to
yourself, to your family,

00:50:52.689 --> 00:50:55.799
to your surroundings but limit it to others.

00:50:55.799 --> 00:50:58.299
When it comes to others
it works out faster

00:50:58.299 --> 00:51:01.569
so you become the joy,
the source of joy.

00:51:01.594 --> 00:51:04.419
Wherever you go people will like you,

00:51:04.424 --> 00:51:06.959
they’ll enjoy your company.
They’ll say, "This person

00:51:06.959 --> 00:51:09.459
is so much changed, he is
such a beautiful person.

00:51:09.459 --> 00:51:11.959
How is it he’s become so nice?”

00:51:11.959 --> 00:51:14.459
Everybody enjoys it.

00:51:14.459 --> 00:51:17.347
This boy, particular boy, Muslim boy,

00:51:17.359 --> 00:51:20.757
he once wanted, his mother
wanted to go to Mecca.

00:51:20.780 --> 00:51:23.719
He said, “Alright. the Mecca is
now in London, let’s go there.”

00:51:23.750 --> 00:51:26.549
And he brought his mother
to Mecca, that was London,

00:51:26.549 --> 00:51:28.859
and he brought her to
me. And she said,

00:51:28.859 --> 00:51:32.029
“Really, I never felt such
joy before going to Mecca,

00:51:32.029 --> 00:51:34.327
the amount of joy I’m feeling here.”

00:51:34.327 --> 00:51:37.429
So he said, “That’s it. I told you
that if you have to have the joy,

00:51:37.429 --> 00:51:39.749
better come to the Mecca
which is real today.”

00:51:39.749 --> 00:51:44.769
That’s what it is, is that
you have to feel that subtle,

00:51:44.796 --> 00:51:47.296
that beautiful

00:51:47.296 --> 00:51:49.179
awareness that is within us,

00:51:49.179 --> 00:51:51.978
just yet to be unfolding itself

00:51:51.978 --> 00:51:55.109
which gives us the sensation,

00:51:55.132 --> 00:51:57.986
the experience of feeling the joy.

00:51:58.652 --> 00:52:01.856
This is what has to happen,
has happened to all of you

00:52:01.856 --> 00:52:04.746
but please remember that you
have to establish yourself.

00:52:04.746 --> 00:52:07.487
Do not fritter it away, it’s
a very precious thing.

00:52:07.487 --> 00:52:10.726
You must respect your Self-realisation.

00:52:10.746 --> 00:52:12.406
Because you don’t pay for it,

00:52:12.406 --> 00:52:14.576
because you have not worked for it

00:52:14.576 --> 00:52:17.076
you do not respect it also.
It’s a very sad thing.

00:52:17.076 --> 00:52:19.576
But you must know
whatever you are today,

00:52:19.576 --> 00:52:22.076
whatever your being is,

00:52:22.076 --> 00:52:25.689
has come to there
without doing any work,

00:52:25.689 --> 00:52:29.339
without paying for it
and it is so important.

00:52:29.381 --> 00:52:32.799
In the same way your
Self-realisation is very important.

00:52:32.831 --> 00:52:35.761
Tomorrow I’ll be leaving for Australia.

00:52:36.181 --> 00:52:39.341
It’s very sad every time I leave the place

00:52:39.371 --> 00:52:42.361
I feel very

00:52:42.381 --> 00:52:44.271
concerned.

00:52:44.271 --> 00:52:46.771
And a concern of a mother is like an ocean

00:52:46.771 --> 00:52:49.271
that just tries to bubble out

00:52:49.271 --> 00:52:51.771
the tears and I don’t
know what to say.

00:52:51.771 --> 00:52:55.451
But I leave it to you

00:52:55.471 --> 00:52:57.971
that you look after yourselves.

00:52:58.771 --> 00:53:02.831
I’ll try to come again
next year to New Zealand.

00:53:02.831 --> 00:53:05.331
By that time I hope you’ll
have many more people

00:53:05.331 --> 00:53:07.831
here who are seekers being saved

00:53:07.831 --> 00:53:10.839
and whom you’ll give Realisation yourself.

00:53:10.839 --> 00:53:13.339
May God bless you all.

00:53:19.776 --> 00:53:22.850
So now we have to just
again feel the experience.

00:53:22.850 --> 00:53:25.974
For about ten minutes it will work out

00:53:26.007 --> 00:53:28.507
and then

00:53:32.047 --> 00:53:34.547
I hope you will make it convenient to

00:53:34.587 --> 00:53:36.957
go to our

00:53:36.997 --> 00:53:38.397
to go to our

00:53:38.414 --> 00:53:40.507
centre. We have a centre here,

00:53:40.507 --> 00:53:43.917
very beautiful centre, and
we have a person like Brian

00:53:43.957 --> 00:53:46.837
who is a very good Sahaja Yogi,

00:53:46.857 --> 00:53:49.357
very well equipped, very learned

00:53:49.357 --> 00:53:52.267
and who will help you in every way.

00:53:52.267 --> 00:53:54.477
We’ll give you the
address of the gentleman

00:53:54.477 --> 00:53:56.977
and you all try to

00:53:56.977 --> 00:53:58.707
do the needful.

00:53:58.707 --> 00:54:01.207
You must know that
Sahaja Yoga is not

00:54:01.207 --> 00:54:03.707
for useless, frivolous

00:54:03.707 --> 00:54:07.267
people, it’s not, it’s
meant for special people.

00:54:07.271 --> 00:54:10.121
It’s a special thing meant for special

00:54:10.141 --> 00:54:12.641
and not for people who are cheap,

00:54:12.641 --> 00:54:15.141
who are frivolous, who are

00:54:15.141 --> 00:54:18.361
good for nothing. So you,

00:54:18.401 --> 00:54:20.171
those who get Realisation,

00:54:20.171 --> 00:54:23.531
know that you are special
people chosen by God

00:54:23.531 --> 00:54:26.901
his gift has come to you
and try to develop it.

00:54:26.901 --> 00:54:29.401
It’s not like any other

00:54:29.401 --> 00:54:31.901
nonsensical thing that
you know of, like

00:54:31.901 --> 00:54:34.401
paying so much money you
become a member and all that.

00:54:34.401 --> 00:54:36.901
You have to become
yourself a Sahaja Yogi,

00:54:36.901 --> 00:54:39.401
it is within yourself but

00:54:39.401 --> 00:54:41.594
it is a state which you have to achieve.

00:54:41.594 --> 00:54:46.331
Unless and until you achieve your state
you cannot just become Mother’s disciple

00:54:46.351 --> 00:54:48.571
or you can wear some dress. No, it is

00:54:48.571 --> 00:54:51.261
something that happens
to you within yourself.

00:54:51.291 --> 00:54:53.381
So first, that has happened
yesterday to you,

00:54:53.381 --> 00:54:56.861
that you’ve became thoughtlessly aware.

00:54:56.861 --> 00:54:59.361
This is called as Nirvichar Samadhi.

00:54:59.361 --> 00:55:04.296
This happens when the Kundalini
rests above the Agnya chakra.

00:55:04.296 --> 00:55:06.796
You did feel the thoughtless
awareness yesterday.

00:55:06.796 --> 00:55:09.296
Now the second state will
be, is called as the

00:55:09.296 --> 00:55:12.996
doubtless awareness which is
called as a Nirvikalpa Samadhi.

00:55:12.996 --> 00:55:15.496
This is all written down in
all the scriptures everywhere

00:55:15.496 --> 00:55:16.786
that these things happen.

00:55:16.786 --> 00:55:18.568
Those of you who also talk of yoga

00:55:18.568 --> 00:55:21.596
must know that Patanjali
who wrote the all of Yoga

00:55:21.596 --> 00:55:23.286
from which they’ve taken a wee bit

00:55:23.291 --> 00:55:25.416
and doing all these practices,

00:55:25.416 --> 00:55:29.076
has at length, he has
described what happens to you

00:55:29.081 --> 00:55:31.236
when you get into the samadhi state:

00:55:31.236 --> 00:55:33.736
the first is the thoughtless
awareness and the second one

00:55:33.736 --> 00:55:35.586
is a doubtless awareness.

00:55:35.586 --> 00:55:37.976
Now this doubtless
awareness is not mental

00:55:37.976 --> 00:55:40.776
that you have no doubts, that’s not the point.

00:55:40.776 --> 00:55:42.676
At the doubtless awareness point

00:55:42.676 --> 00:55:45.036
you start giving Realization
to others, you start

00:55:45.036 --> 00:55:47.536
curing people, you start knowing

00:55:47.536 --> 00:55:50.036
the knowledge by yourself

00:55:50.036 --> 00:55:52.536
and that is the state one must achieve.

00:55:52.536 --> 00:55:55.506
Once you achieve that state
then you are perfected.

00:55:55.506 --> 00:55:58.006
Like a little seed which has sprouted

00:55:58.006 --> 00:56:01.226
is very delicate. And this seed

00:56:01.246 --> 00:56:03.746
which has sprouted has
to be looked after and

00:56:03.746 --> 00:56:06.846
that seed has to be

00:56:06.856 --> 00:56:09.356
taken in such a way that it requires

00:56:09.356 --> 00:56:11.856
all the attention, all
the respect. And then

00:56:11.856 --> 00:56:14.356
when it is grows into a proper tree

00:56:14.356 --> 00:56:16.326
you don’t have to worry.

00:56:16.326 --> 00:56:18.826
Then you become the tree

00:56:18.826 --> 00:56:21.326
of love and compassion
and so many come

00:56:21.326 --> 00:56:26.369
and sit under this tree to
enjoy that beauty that you are.

00:56:27.809 --> 00:56:30.309
So today again we’ll have the same

00:56:30.309 --> 00:56:32.809
experience we had to again

00:56:32.809 --> 00:56:35.309
to establish our Realisation.

00:56:38.229 --> 00:56:41.624
Now I have to make one
humble request again

00:56:41.624 --> 00:56:43.763
that we have to take out our shoes

00:56:43.775 --> 00:56:45.353
to touch the Mother Earth,

00:56:45.344 --> 00:56:47.844
it’s important just to
touch our Mother Earth

00:56:47.844 --> 00:56:51.753
we must take out our shoes, if
possible, it will be a good idea.

00:57:09.976 --> 00:57:12.476
Now you have to just put

00:57:12.476 --> 00:57:14.976
your both the hands
towards me to begin with

00:57:16.786 --> 00:57:19.876
just both the hands towards me.

00:57:19.876 --> 00:57:22.376
Now this hand represents
the left side and this

00:57:22.376 --> 00:57:24.876
side represents the
right side, means

00:57:24.876 --> 00:57:28.306
this (left side) represents your
desire and the right is your action.

00:57:28.301 --> 00:57:31.346
So it is you who has to raise your Kundalini.

00:57:32.886 --> 00:57:35.386
I am not going to raise it.
It is you who must learn

00:57:35.386 --> 00:57:39.561
how to raise your own Kundalini
and manoeuvre the power yourself.

00:57:39.585 --> 00:57:42.085
So the first thing is to put the left hand

00:57:42.085 --> 00:57:44.585
towards me like this, just like this.

00:57:44.585 --> 00:57:47.645
You have to put the hand
towards me like this,

00:57:49.975 --> 00:57:52.475
on your lap. Sit comfortably putting the

00:57:52.475 --> 00:57:54.975
left hand on your left lap

00:57:56.715 --> 00:57:59.215
towards me like this.

00:58:00.415 --> 00:58:02.915
With the right hand you have to move,

00:58:02.915 --> 00:58:05.415
you have to move your
different centres

00:58:05.415 --> 00:58:07.915
which is very simple. First of all

00:58:07.915 --> 00:58:11.763
you’ll have to put the right hand on
your heart where resides the Spirit.

00:58:11.796 --> 00:58:14.893
Then you’ll have to put ... I’ll
tell you later on one by one,

00:58:14.893 --> 00:58:17.393
on the upper part of
the stomach where resides

00:58:17.393 --> 00:58:19.893
the principle of mastery

00:58:19.893 --> 00:58:22.393
and then in the lower
part of the abdomen

00:58:22.393 --> 00:58:24.893
where resides the technique,

00:58:24.893 --> 00:58:27.393
the knowledge of the technique

00:58:27.393 --> 00:58:30.553
of manoeuvring this power.

00:58:30.553 --> 00:58:34.583
Because, as I told you yesterday,
yoga means union with the Divine

00:58:34.583 --> 00:58:38.000
and another thing yoga
means – the trick,

00:58:38.000 --> 00:58:41.073
or the yukti as they call it,

00:58:41.090 --> 00:58:44.593
deftness to handle the
power that flows through you,

00:58:44.593 --> 00:58:47.093
to understand how to protect yourself,

00:58:47.093 --> 00:58:49.889
how to raise your Kundalini,

00:58:49.889 --> 00:58:54.119
how to work it out. That part
is called as pure knowledge

00:58:54.159 --> 00:58:56.659
and that, the centre it resides

00:58:56.659 --> 00:58:59.920
in the lower part of your
abdomen on the left-hand side.

00:59:00.938 --> 00:59:03.438
For information, in the Universe

00:59:03.438 --> 00:59:06.690
it is your country, New
Zealand, that works it out.

00:59:06.690 --> 00:59:09.190
Can you imagine that you
stand for auspiciousness,

00:59:09.190 --> 00:59:13.500
this country stands for
auspiciousness, it emits auspiciousness

00:59:13.545 --> 00:59:15.710
for the whole universe.

00:59:15.732 --> 00:59:20.952
It’s such a great country you are
living here that emits auspiciousness.

00:59:20.954 --> 00:59:23.454
So now

00:59:23.454 --> 00:59:26.862
you put your right hand
on your heart, as I said,

00:59:26.862 --> 00:59:30.230
then on the abdomen lower
and then you go back again

00:59:30.274 --> 00:59:34.874
and then you put your
right hand on your neck,

00:59:34.908 --> 00:59:37.408
on the corner of the neck

00:59:37.408 --> 00:59:40.900
and the shoulder, a little backward like
this because this is very important.

00:59:40.909 --> 00:59:43.409
Some people do it from this
side. Do it from this side,

00:59:43.409 --> 00:59:45.845
in front you should bring
it and press it hard,

00:59:45.845 --> 00:59:48.345
this is very important. This centre is

00:59:48.345 --> 00:59:50.845
mostly spoiled in the
West because people have

00:59:50.845 --> 00:59:52.089
a habit of feeling guilty.

00:59:52.105 --> 00:59:54.269
I don’t know why they feel so guilty.

00:59:54.269 --> 00:59:56.399
So at the very outset I tell everybody

00:59:56.411 --> 00:59:58.911
that you tell yourself
you are not guilty because

00:59:58.911 --> 01:00:02.731
you are the temple of God and you
must have full confidence in you.

01:00:02.731 --> 01:00:05.231
Not to feel guilty at all, it’s very important.

01:00:05.231 --> 01:00:07.611
You have to sit with a very

01:00:07.611 --> 01:00:10.111
pleasant disposition that
you are going to enter

01:00:10.111 --> 01:00:11.762
into the Kingdom of God.

01:00:11.762 --> 01:00:14.262
Then the hand goes here,
upon the forehead,

01:00:14.262 --> 01:00:16.762
then goes at the back here and then

01:00:16.762 --> 01:00:19.262
this palm

01:00:19.262 --> 01:00:22.372
has to be pressed on
the fontanel bone area

01:00:22.372 --> 01:00:24.872
where you had a soft
bone as a child and

01:00:24.872 --> 01:00:27.372
you have to press it
clockwise like this.

01:00:28.260 --> 01:00:31.660
Now I’ll just tell you
in a very simple way

01:00:31.684 --> 01:00:33.570
but you have to keep your eyes shut.

01:00:33.570 --> 01:00:37.030
Please take out your spectacles also
because this helps the eyesight.

01:00:37.030 --> 01:00:39.060
So please take out your spectacles,

01:00:39.063 --> 01:00:45.241
don’t put it in the pockets because
you have to put the hand on the heart.

01:00:45.261 --> 01:00:48.681
So please close your eyes now
just, and don’t open your eyes.

01:00:48.681 --> 01:00:51.181
At any cost you should
not open your eyes

01:00:51.181 --> 01:00:56.619
because this is Antar Yoga, it is an
inner happening that takes place.

01:00:56.619 --> 01:00:58.519
For that if you open your eyes

01:00:58.519 --> 01:01:01.019
then the attention goes
out so please keep your

01:01:01.019 --> 01:01:04.204
eyes shut till you have
achieved your Realisation.

01:01:04.204 --> 01:01:06.109
I’ll tell you when to open your eyes.

01:01:06.109 --> 01:01:09.209
Now put your right hand on your heart,

01:01:09.229 --> 01:01:11.839
right hand on your heart

01:01:11.839 --> 01:01:14.339
and left hand towards
me. Everyone should do it,

01:01:15.139 --> 01:01:19.599
pay attention to yourself, don’t
worry anybody or anybody else.

01:01:19.609 --> 01:01:21.149
Just now think of yourself.

01:01:21.153 --> 01:01:24.823
Put your right hand on your heart.

01:01:24.846 --> 01:01:27.346
Here resides the Spirit.

01:01:27.346 --> 01:01:29.846
So first you ask me a question,

01:01:29.846 --> 01:01:34.726
a very fundamental question. You can call me
“Mother” or you can call me “Shri Mataji”,

01:01:34.726 --> 01:01:37.076
whatever suits you,

01:01:37.076 --> 01:01:39.576
Shri Mataji, am I the Spirit?”

01:01:39.576 --> 01:01:43.166
Ask a question three times.

01:01:43.166 --> 01:01:45.666
Inside your heart ask a question,

01:01:45.666 --> 01:01:48.786
“Shri Mataji, am I the Spirit?

01:01:50.756 --> 01:01:53.256
Mother, am I the Spirit?”

01:02:08.384 --> 01:02:10.544
This question relates to another thing,

01:02:10.543 --> 01:02:12.864
that if you are your Spirit

01:02:12.864 --> 01:02:15.364
you are your master,

01:02:15.364 --> 01:02:18.264
you are your guide, you are your guru.

01:02:18.274 --> 01:02:23.524
So now you put this right hand in the upper
part of the abdomen on the left-hand side

01:02:23.524 --> 01:02:27.424
and press it. Here is
the centre of the Guru.

01:02:27.464 --> 01:02:32.074
So now here you ask a question,
“Mother, am I my own guru?

01:02:32.107 --> 01:02:34.607
Mother, am I my own master?

01:02:34.607 --> 01:02:37.343
Mother, am I my own guide?”

01:02:37.397 --> 01:02:40.663
ask the question ten times,
anyone that you want to ask.

01:02:40.673 --> 01:02:44.363
Ten times because as I told
you there are ten valences

01:02:44.398 --> 01:02:46.898
and once you have

01:02:46.898 --> 01:02:51.491
awakened those ten valences you’ve
become the master, the guru.

01:02:54.370 --> 01:02:56.870
Please ask three times.

01:03:09.480 --> 01:03:12.412
Now

01:03:12.428 --> 01:03:14.468
take this right hand

01:03:14.490 --> 01:03:17.958
in the lower part of your abdomen,

01:03:17.958 --> 01:03:19.818
on the left hand side;

01:03:19.818 --> 01:03:24.928
lower part of your left hand side stomach.

01:03:24.940 --> 01:03:28.598
Please put this hand and press it, little bit.

01:03:28.608 --> 01:03:31.918
At this centre resides, as I told you,

01:03:31.926 --> 01:03:34.588
is the technique, is the true knowledge,

01:03:34.588 --> 01:03:37.088
the pure knowledge. But

01:03:37.098 --> 01:03:40.348
I cannot cross your freedom,

01:03:40.368 --> 01:03:42.598
so you have to say,

01:03:42.619 --> 01:03:45.119
you have to

01:03:46.139 --> 01:03:48.639
say it that you want

01:03:48.669 --> 01:03:50.239
the true knowledge.

01:03:50.260 --> 01:03:52.760
I cannot force on you so please say,

01:03:52.760 --> 01:03:56.730
“Mother, I want true knowledge.”

01:03:59.709 --> 01:04:03.728
Shuddha Vidya. “I want pure knowledge.

01:04:03.746 --> 01:04:08.316
Please give me, Mother please
give me pure knowledge”.

01:04:08.339 --> 01:04:10.839
You have to say it six times.

01:04:10.839 --> 01:04:14.243
This is the way you actually

01:04:14.279 --> 01:04:17.253
awaken the Kundalini to begin with.

01:04:17.259 --> 01:04:19.759
“Please give me pure knowledge.”

01:04:30.589 --> 01:04:33.089
Put both the hands  on the ground

01:04:33.089 --> 01:04:35.722
in a parallel way, don’t touch each other

01:04:35.722 --> 01:04:38.720
and please touch the Mother Earth.

01:04:41.842 --> 01:04:44.342
Sit very comfortably (Warren interrupts
"With your feet on") No, no, no.

01:04:44.342 --> 01:04:47.741
with your feet, with your feet. Touch
the Mother Earth with your feet.

01:04:47.737 --> 01:04:50.237
Now, with your feet.

01:04:54.097 --> 01:04:56.597
Say it six times

01:04:58.066 --> 01:05:01.331
as a request because I cannot

01:05:01.356 --> 01:05:04.971
force it on you, you have to ask for it.

01:05:11.331 --> 01:05:15.630
Now raise this right hand again back

01:05:15.630 --> 01:05:18.361
onto the upper part of the abdomen.

01:05:19.591 --> 01:05:22.190
As the Kundalini has started moving

01:05:23.320 --> 01:05:26.101
now you have to assert

01:05:26.121 --> 01:05:28.880
yourself with full confidence.

01:05:28.880 --> 01:05:32.221
At this point you have to say ten times,

01:05:32.251 --> 01:05:34.681
“Mother, I am my own master.

01:05:34.681 --> 01:05:37.771
Mother, I am my own guru.

01:05:37.791 --> 01:05:41.261
Mother, I am my guide.” Say it ten times.

01:05:44.225 --> 01:05:47.250
Assert with full confidence.

01:05:48.210 --> 01:05:50.710
Put the hand on the right hand side

01:05:50.710 --> 01:05:53.455
of your stomach

01:05:53.490 --> 01:05:55.990
on the left hand side.

01:05:55.990 --> 01:06:02.037
You put your right hand on the
left-hand side of your stomach,

01:06:02.057 --> 01:06:04.557
on the upper part, on the upper part,

01:06:04.557 --> 01:06:08.437
that is the centre for the Guru.

01:06:08.457 --> 01:06:11.097
So here you have to say ten times

01:06:12.157 --> 01:06:17.893
with full confidence,
“Mother, I am my own master.

01:06:17.903 --> 01:06:20.403
I am my own guru.”

01:06:43.483 --> 01:06:45.983
Now raise your right hand

01:06:48.763 --> 01:06:50.895
to your heart again.

01:06:50.895 --> 01:06:53.395
Now at the point of heart

01:06:53.395 --> 01:06:55.895
you have to again

01:06:55.895 --> 01:07:00.370
assert and accept with confidence

01:07:00.401 --> 01:07:04.100
and say, “Mother,

01:07:04.121 --> 01:07:07.695
I am the Spirit.” Say it twelve times,

01:07:07.695 --> 01:07:10.195
“Mother, I am the Spirit.” which you are,

01:07:10.195 --> 01:07:13.375
just you must assert.

01:07:13.385 --> 01:07:15.665
You must accept, “I am the Spirit.”

01:07:15.665 --> 01:07:18.165
Have full confidence in yourself,

01:07:18.165 --> 01:07:20.965
you are not to feel guilty
at all and you have to say

01:07:20.975 --> 01:07:23.165
that, “Mother, I am the Spirit.”

01:07:25.385 --> 01:07:28.865
So the Kundalini rises with that assertion.

01:07:51.076 --> 01:07:55.536
Now put the right hand

01:07:55.546 --> 01:07:58.426
on the shoulder

01:07:58.446 --> 01:08:00.946
near the neck, press it hard.

01:08:00.946 --> 01:08:03.446
This is the centre... from
the front, as I said,

01:08:03.446 --> 01:08:05.946
not from the backside,
from the front. And now

01:08:05.946 --> 01:08:08.637
press it hard, this is a very important centre

01:08:08.646 --> 01:08:11.757
because, as I told you,
people who feel guilty

01:08:11.776 --> 01:08:15.067
have this problem and the
Kundalini doesn’t rise.

01:08:15.107 --> 01:08:17.607
So please say sixteen times,

01:08:17.607 --> 01:08:21.741
“Mother, I am not guilty at all.”

01:08:23.206 --> 01:08:27.601
We have to know that
God is the ocean of love

01:08:27.601 --> 01:08:30.726
and is the ocean of compassion

01:08:30.741 --> 01:08:34.966
but above all he is the ocean of forgiveness,

01:08:34.966 --> 01:08:38.196
he is the ocean. And
whatever we may do

01:08:38.226 --> 01:08:41.696
he is quite capable and powerful to forgive us.

01:08:41.696 --> 01:08:43.976
We must learn to forgive
ourselves first of all,

01:08:43.976 --> 01:08:46.026
we don’t know how to
forgive ourselves.

01:08:46.026 --> 01:08:49.316
So please forgive yourself
and say sixteen times,

01:08:49.332 --> 01:08:52.684
“Mother, I am not guilty at all.”

01:08:52.690 --> 01:08:56.394
Because, as I said, you
are the temple of God,

01:08:56.414 --> 01:08:58.914
how can you be guilty?

01:09:01.274 --> 01:09:03.774
Sixteen times.

01:09:07.430 --> 01:09:09.930
Better?  [Warren: "Um it's still there."]

01:09:11.257 --> 01:09:14.566
Still there, it's still
there, please go on saying

01:09:14.566 --> 01:09:18.037
with full understanding.

01:09:19.199 --> 01:09:20.848
From your heart please say it.

01:09:20.848 --> 01:09:23.348
Because if you have
this centre catching

01:09:23.348 --> 01:09:28.758
it will be difficult for me, for
you, to get your Realisation.

01:09:28.778 --> 01:09:31.978
So please say it from your heart,

01:09:31.998 --> 01:09:34.498
from your heart.

01:09:38.474 --> 01:09:40.344
Hmm better.

01:09:40.378 --> 01:09:42.878
Those who still think they are guilty

01:09:42.878 --> 01:09:45.378
should punish themselves
by saying it 108 times,

01:09:45.378 --> 01:09:48.564
that would be a better idea.

01:09:48.588 --> 01:09:51.494
Be pleasant about it, be
pleasant about yourself.

01:09:51.494 --> 01:09:55.024
Why do you want to condemn
yourself for nothing at all?

01:09:56.008 --> 01:10:00.018
God has not created you
to condemn yourself.

01:10:05.048 --> 01:10:07.548
Ha!

01:10:07.548 --> 01:10:12.436
Now raise your right hand
to your forehead across

01:10:12.441 --> 01:10:15.480
and press it from both the ends

01:10:15.521 --> 01:10:18.090
as if when we have a
headache we press it.

01:10:18.090 --> 01:10:21.180
Just press it and here you have to say,

01:10:21.210 --> 01:10:24.730
“Mother, I forgive everyone.”

01:10:24.760 --> 01:10:27.260
As soon as it works out

01:10:27.260 --> 01:10:29.960
I will know that you have said it.
How many times is not the point.

01:10:29.980 --> 01:10:34.256
Press it hard. “Mother,
I forgive everyone.”

01:10:34.256 --> 01:10:36.220
Now many people feel that to forgive….

01:10:36.220 --> 01:10:41.558
Yesterday everybody who did not get
Realisation had not forgiven people.

01:10:41.588 --> 01:10:43.948
I told you that it’s a myth.

01:10:43.948 --> 01:10:48.478
You do not do anything when you
forgive or when you don’t forgive.

01:10:48.478 --> 01:10:50.588
Only thing when you don’t forgive

01:10:50.588 --> 01:10:53.088
you play into the hands of the people

01:10:53.088 --> 01:10:54.988
who are trying to do you wrong.

01:10:54.995 --> 01:10:57.495
So why do you want to play into
the hands of the wrong people?

01:10:57.495 --> 01:11:02.358
Just say, “I forgive” and
you’ll be clearly out of it.

01:11:02.378 --> 01:11:06.088
It’s only you who is maintaining
that by not forgiving.

01:11:06.093 --> 01:11:09.958
It’s a myth, it’s absolutely
a myth. But just say it

01:11:09.968 --> 01:11:12.268
that, “Mother, I forgive everyone.”

01:11:12.268 --> 01:11:15.855
Nothing is difficult because
you are not doing about it,

01:11:15.881 --> 01:11:18.381
just by saying what do you do?
